Notation "a # b" := (a b) (at level 1, only parsing) : asm.
Notation "a # b <- c" := (Pregmap.set b c a) (at level 1, b at next level) : asm.

Open Scope asm.

Ltac split_and :=
  repeat match goal with
  | |- ?A /\ ?B => split
  end.

Tactic Notation "destruct_in" hyp(H) "eq:" ident(EQ) :=
  let ty := type of H in
  match ty with
  | context[match ?X with
            | _ => _
            end] => destruct X eqn:EQ
  end.

isize for THUMB and wsize for THUMB-2
Definition isize := Ptrofs.repr 2.
Definition wsize := Ptrofs.repr 4.


Abstract semantics.

We augment values with symbolic values.
Inductive sreg :=
| Sreg : preg -> sreg
| Ssp.

Inductive sval :=
| Sval (base: sreg) (ofs: Ptrofs.int)
| Rval (base:sreg).

Inductive aval :=
| Cval (v:val)
| Aval (v:sval).


Definition typ_of_preg (p:preg) : typ :=
  match p with
  | IR _ => Tany32
  | FR _ => Tany64
  | CR _ => Tany32
  | PC => Tany32
  end.

Definition typ_of_sreg (v:sreg) :=
  match v with
  | Sreg r => typ_of_preg r
  | Ssp => Tany32
  end.

Definition typ_of_sval (v:sval) :=
  match v with
  | Sval _ _ => Tany32
  | Rval p => typ_of_sreg p
  end.

Definition aregset := Pregmap.t aval.

Inductive rchunk := Cany32 | Cint32.

Inductive amemval :=
| Cmemval (v:memval)
| Amemval (sv:sval) (rc:rchunk) (n:nat).



Definition sreg_eq (r r' : sreg) : bool :=
  match r , r' with
  | Sreg r1 , Sreg r2 => preg_eq r1 r2
  | Ssp , Ssp => true
  | _ , _ => false
  end.

Definition sval_eq (sv sv': sval) :=
  match sv , sv' with
  | Sval b o , Sval b' o' => sreg_eq b b' && Ptrofs.eq o o'
  | Rval r , Rval r' => sreg_eq r r'
  | _ , _ => false
  end.

Definition aval_eq (v1 v2 : aval) : bool :=
  match v1 , v2 with
  | Aval v1 , Aval v2 => sval_eq v1 v2
  | Cval v1 , Cval v2 => Val.eq v1 v2
  | _ , _ => false
  end.

Definition find_instr (v:aval) (m:mem) : option (instruction * bool) :=
  match v with
  | Cval v => find_instr v m
  | _ => None
  end.


We model an abstract stack frame. This is a memory block containing abstract memory values.

This behaves as Fragments, endianness is ignored

Definition encode_sval_fragments (rc:rchunk) (r:sval) := ((Amemval r rc 3)::(Amemval r rc 2)::(Amemval r rc 1)::(Amemval r rc 0)::nil)%nat.

Definition rchunk_of_chunk (chunk: memory_chunk) :=
  match chunk with
  | Many32 => Some Cany32
  | Mint32 => Some Cint32
  | _ => None
  end.


Definition encode_sval (chunk: memory_chunk) (r:sval) : option (list amemval) :=
  match typ_of_sval r with
  | Tany32 =>
      match rchunk_of_chunk chunk with
      | Some rc => Some (encode_sval_fragments rc r)
      | None => None
      end
  | _ => None
  end.

Definition encode_aval (chunk: memory_chunk) (v : aval) : option (list amemval) :=
  match v with
  | Cval v => Some (List.map Cmemval (encode_val chunk v))
  | Aval r => encode_sval chunk r
  end.


Fixpoint setN (vl : list amemval) (p : Z) (c : ZMap.t amemval) {struct vl} : ZMap.t amemval :=
  match vl with
  | nil => c
  | v :: vl' => setN vl' (p + 1) (ZMap.set p v c)
  end.

Fixpoint getN (n : nat) (p : Z) (c : ZMap.t amemval) {struct n} : list amemval :=
  match n with
  | 0%nat => nil
  | Datatypes.S n' => ZMap.get p c :: getN n' (p + 1) c
  end.

Definition astack_store (chunk: memory_chunk) (m:mem) (mb: ZMap.t amemval) (b:block) (ofs:Z) (v:aval) :=
  match Mem.valid_access_dec m chunk b ofs Writable with
  | left _ => match encode_aval chunk v with
              | None => None
              | Some ec =>
                  Some (setN ec ofs mb)
              end
  | right _ => None
  end.

Inductive AmemSplit : Type :=
| SplitErr
| SplitNIL
| SplitC (l: list memval)
| SplitA (l: list (sval * rchunk * nat)).

Definition cons_amemval (m:amemval) (s : AmemSplit) :=
  match s with
  | SplitErr => SplitErr
  | SplitNIL => match m with
                | Cmemval x => SplitC (x::nil)
                | Amemval s rc o => SplitA ((s,rc,o)::nil)
                end
  | SplitC l => match m with
                | Cmemval x => SplitC (x::l)
                | Amemval _ _ _ => SplitErr
                end
  | SplitA l => match m with
                | Cmemval x => SplitErr
                | Amemval s rc o => SplitA ((s,rc, o)::l)
                end
  end.


Definition rchunk_eq (x y: rchunk) : {x = y} + {x <> y}.
Proof.
  decide equality.
Defined.

Fixpoint split_amemval (l: list amemval) : AmemSplit :=
  match l with
  | nil => SplitNIL
  | e::l => cons_amemval e (split_amemval l)
  end.

Fixpoint check_value (n:nat) (v: sval) (rc:rchunk) (vl: list (sval * rchunk * nat)) :=
  match n with
  | O => match vl with
         | nil => true
         | _ :: _ => false
         end
  | Datatypes.S m => match vl with
           | (v',rc',idx)::vl' => sval_eq v v' && rchunk_eq rc rc' && (m =? idx)%nat && check_value m v rc vl'
           | _ => false
           end
  end.





Definition proj_value (chunk: memory_chunk) (vl:list (sval * rchunk * nat)) : option aval :=
  match rchunk_of_chunk chunk with
  | None => None
  | Some rc0 =>
      match vl with
      | (v,rc, _) :: _ => if rchunk_eq rc0 rc && check_value 4%nat v rc vl then Some (Aval v) else None
      | _ => None
      end
  end.


Definition decode_val (chunk:memory_chunk) (vl: list amemval) :=
  match split_amemval vl with
  | SplitErr => None
  | SplitNIL => None
  | SplitC l => Some (Cval (decode_val chunk l))
  | SplitA l => proj_value chunk l
  end.

Definition astack_load (chunk: memory_chunk) (m:mem) (mb: ZMap.t amemval) (b:block) (ofs:Z) :=
  if Mem.valid_access_dec m chunk b ofs Readable
  then decode_val chunk (getN (size_chunk_nat chunk) ofs mb)
  else None.

Definition astack := ZMap.t amemval.

Inductive aoutcome : Type :=
| ANext : aregset -> astack -> block -> mem -> aoutcome
| AStuck : aoutcome.


Definition alift1 (f: val -> val) (v : aval) : aval :=
  match v with
  | Cval v => Cval (f v)
  | _ => Cval Vundef
  end.


Definition ashl (v:aval) (i:int) := alift1 (fun v => Val.shl v (Vint i)) v.

Definition ashru (v:aval) (i:int) :=alift1 (fun v => Val.shru v (Vint i)) v.

Definition ashr (v:aval) (i:int) := alift1 (fun v => Val.shr v (Vint i)) v.

Definition aror (v:aval) (i:int) := alift1 (fun v => Val.ror v (Vint i)) v.

Definition aeval_shift_op (so: shift_op) (rs: aregset) :=
  match so with
  | SOimm n => Cval (Vint n)
  | SOreg r => rs r
  | SOlsl r n => ashl (rs r) n
  | SOlsr r n => ashru (rs r) n
  | SOasr r n => ashr (rs r) n
  | SOror r n => aror (rs r) n
  end.

Definition aadd (v1 v2: aval) : option aval :=
  match v1 , v2 with
  | Cval v1 , Cval v2 => Some (Cval (Val.add v1 v2))
  | Aval (Sval r o) , Cval (Vint i)
  | Cval (Vint i) , Aval (Sval r o)
                      => Some (Aval (Sval r (Ptrofs.add o (Ptrofs.of_int i))))
  | _ , _ => None
  end.

Definition alift2 (f: val -> val -> val) (v1 v2 : aval) : aval :=
  match v1 , v2 with
  | Cval v1 , Cval v2 => Cval (f v1 v2)
  | _ , _ => Cval Vundef
  end.



Definition aoffset_ptr (v:aval) (ofs : ptrofs) : aval :=
  match v with
  | Cval v => Cval (Val.offset_ptr v ofs)
  | Aval (Sval r o) => Aval (Sval r (Ptrofs.add o ofs))
  | Aval (Rval r) => Cval Vundef
  end.


the jump case always uses isize, by default
Definition agoto_label (lbl: ptrofs) (rs:aregset) (b: block) (stk : astack) (m: mem) :=
  ANext (rs#PC <- (aoffset_ptr rs#PC (Ptrofs.add (Ptrofs.mul lbl isize) wsize))) stk b m.


Definition size_of_bool (is_32bits :bool) :=
  if is_32bits then wsize else isize.

Definition anextinstr (is_32bits:bool) (rs: aregset) :=
  rs#PC <- (aoffset_ptr rs#PC (size_of_bool is_32bits)).

Definition incrinstr (rs: aregset) :=
  rs#PC <- (aoffset_ptr rs#PC Ptrofs.one).


Definition aundef_flags (rs: aregset) : aregset :=
  fun r => match r with CR _ => Cval Vundef | _ => rs r end.

Definition anextinstr_nf (is_wide: bool) (rs: aregset) :=
  anextinstr is_wide (aundef_flags rs).

Definition acompare_int (rs:aregset) (v1 v2: aval) (m:mem) :=
  rs#CN <- (alift1 Val.negative (alift2 Val.sub v1 v2))
    #CZ <- (alift2 (Val.cmpu (Mem.valid_pointer m) Ceq) v1 v2)
    #CC <- (alift2 (Val.cmpu (Mem.valid_pointer m) Cge) v1 v2)
    #CV <- (alift2 Val.sub_overflow v1 v2).

Definition get_offset (v:sval) : Ptrofs.int :=
  match v with
  | Rval _ => Ptrofs.zero
  | Sval _ ofs => ofs
  end.

Definition get_register (v:sval) : sreg :=
  match v with
  | Rval r | Sval r _ => r
  end.

Definition get_stack_offset (v:sval) : option Ptrofs.int :=
  if sreg_eq Ssp (get_register v)
  then Some (get_offset v)
  else None.

we consider ldr is always 32-bit
Definition aexec_load (is_32bits:bool) (chunk: memory_chunk) (addr: option aval) (r: preg)
                     (rs: aregset) (stk:astack) (b: block) (m: mem) :=
  match addr with
  | Some (Cval addr') =>
      match Mem.loadv chunk m addr' with
      | None => AStuck
      | Some v => ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r <- (Cval v))) stk b m
      end
  | Some (Aval sv) => match get_stack_offset sv with
               | Some o =>
                      match astack_load chunk m stk b (Ptrofs.unsigned o) with
                      | None => AStuck
                      | Some v => ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r <- v)) stk b m
                      end
               | _ => AStuck
               end
  | None => AStuck
  end.

Definition is_stack_pointer (stkb: block) (av:aval) : option Ptrofs.int :=
  match av with
  | Aval sv => get_stack_offset sv
  | Cval a => match a with
              | Vptr b o => if eq_block b stkb then Some o else None
              | _ => None
              end
  end.

Definition aexec_store' (chunk: memory_chunk) (addr: option aval) (r: preg)
                      (rs: aregset) (stk: astack) (b:block) (m: mem) :=
  match addr with
  | None => AStuck
  | Some av =>
      match is_stack_pointer b av with
      | Some o =>
          match astack_store chunk m stk b (Ptrofs.unsigned o) (rs r) with
          | None => AStuck
          | Some stk' => ANext rs stk' b m
          end
      | None =>
          match av , rs r with
          | (Cval addr') , Cval v =>
              match Mem.storev chunk m addr' v with
              | None => AStuck
              | Some m' => ANext rs stk b m'
              end
          | _ , _ => AStuck
          end
      end
  end.

we consider str is always 32-bit
Definition aexec_store (is_32bits:bool) (chunk: memory_chunk) (addr: option aval) (r: preg)
                      (rs: aregset) (stk: astack) (b:block) (m: mem) :=
  match aexec_store' chunk addr r rs stk b m with
  | AStuck => AStuck
  | ANext rs' stk' stkb m' => ANext (anextinstr is_32bits rs') stk' stkb m'
  end.

Definition adivs (v1 v2:aval) : option aval :=
  match v1 , v2 with
  | Cval v1 , Cval v2 => match Val.divs v1 v2 with
                       | None => None
                       | Some v => Some (Cval v)
                       end
  | _ , _ => None
  end.

Definition adivu (v1 v2:aval) : option aval :=
  match v1 , v2 with
  | Cval v1 , Cval v2 => match Val.divu v1 v2 with
                       | None => None
                       | Some v => Some (Cval v)
                       end
  | _ , _ => None
  end.


Fixpoint update_regset (vl:list (preg * aval)) (rs :aregset) :=
  match vl with
  | nil => rs
  | (r,v)::vl => (update_regset vl rs) # r <- v
  end.

Definition init_regset (vl:list (preg * val)) (rs :aregset) :=
  update_regset (List.map (fun '(r,v) => (r,Cval v)) vl) rs.

Definition acompare_float_update (v1 v2: aval) :=
  match v1 , v2 with
  | Cval (Vfloat f1), Cval (Vfloat f2) =>
      (CR CV, (Cval (Val.of_bool (negb (Float.cmp Ceq f1 f2 || Float.cmp Clt f1 f2 || Float.cmp Cgt f1 f2)))))
        :: (CR CC, (Cval (Val.of_bool (negb (Float.cmp Clt f1 f2)))))
        :: (CR CZ, (Cval (Val.of_bool (Float.cmp Ceq f1 f2))))
        :: (CR CN, (Cval (Val.of_bool (Float.cmp Clt f1 f2)))) :: nil
  | _, _ =>
      (CR CV , (Cval Vundef))
        :: (CR CC , (Cval Vundef))
        :: (CR CZ , (Cval Vundef))
        :: (CR CN, (Cval Vundef)) :: nil
  end.

Definition acompare_float (rs: aregset) (v1 v2: aval) :=
  update_regset (acompare_float_update v1 v2) rs.

Definition acompare_float32_update (v1 v2 : aval) :=
  match v1, v2 with
  | Cval (Vsingle f1), Cval (Vsingle f2) =>
      (CR CV ,
        (Cval (Val.of_bool (negb
                              (Float32.cmp Ceq f1 f2 || Float32.cmp Clt f1 f2 || Float32.cmp Cgt f1 f2)))))
        :: (CR CC , (Cval (Val.of_bool (negb (Float32.cmp Clt f1 f2)))))
        :: (CR CZ , (Cval (Val.of_bool (Float32.cmp Ceq f1 f2))))
        ::(CR CN ,(Cval (Val.of_bool (Float32.cmp Clt f1 f2))))
        :: nil
  | _, _ =>
      (CR CV , (Cval Vundef)) ::
        (CR CC , (Cval Vundef)) ::
        (CR CZ , (Cval Vundef)) ::
        (CR CN , (Cval Vundef)) :: nil
  end.

Definition acompare_float32 (rs: aregset) (v1 v2 : aval) :=
  update_regset (acompare_float32_update v1 v2) rs.

Definition amaketotal (ov : option aval) :=
  match ov with
  | Some v => v
  | None => Cval Vundef
  end.

Definition alifto1 (f: val -> option val) (v:aval) : option aval :=
  match v with
  | Cval v => option_map Cval (f v)
  | _ => None
  end.

Definition eval_unary_cond (F : int -> bool) (rs : aregset) (r : preg) :=
  match rs r with
  | Cval (Vint n) => Some (F n)
  | _ => None
  end.

Definition eval_binary_cond (f : int -> int -> bool) (rs : aregset) (r1 : preg) (r2: preg) :=
  match rs r1, rs r2 with
  | Cval (Vint c), Cval(Vint z) => Some (f c z)
  | _, _ => None
  end.

Definition eval_ternary_cond (f : int -> int -> int -> bool) (rs : aregset) (r1 r2 r3: preg) :=
  match rs r1 with
  | Cval (Vint c) => eval_binary_cond (f c) rs r2 r3
  | _ => None
  end.


Definition aeval_testcond (c: testcond) (rs: aregset) : option bool :=
  match c with
  | TCeq => (* equal *)
      eval_unary_cond (Int.eq Int.one) rs CZ
  | TCne => (* not equal *)
      eval_unary_cond (Int.eq Int.zero) rs CZ
  | TClo => (* unsigned less than *)
      eval_unary_cond (Int.eq Int.zero) rs CC
  | TCls => (* unsigned less or equal *)
      eval_binary_cond (fun c z =>
                          (Int.eq c Int.zero || Int.eq z Int.one)) rs CC CZ
  | TChs => (* unsigned greater or equal *)
      eval_unary_cond (Int.eq Int.one) rs CC
  | TChi => (* unsigned greater *)
      eval_binary_cond (fun c z => (Int.eq c Int.one && Int.eq z Int.zero)) rs CC CZ
  | TClt => (* signed less than *)
      eval_binary_cond (fun o s => (Int.eq (Int.xor o s) Int.one)) rs CV CN
  | TCle => (* signed less or equal *)
      eval_ternary_cond (fun o s z => (Int.eq (Int.xor o s) Int.one || Int.eq z Int.one)) rs CV CN CZ
  | TCge => (* signed greater or equal *)
      eval_binary_cond (fun o s => (Int.eq (Int.xor o s) Int.zero)) rs CV CN
  | TCgt => (* signed greater *)
      eval_ternary_cond (fun o s z => (Int.eq (Int.xor o s) Int.zero && Int.eq z Int.zero)) rs CV CN CZ
  | TCpl => (* positive *)
      eval_unary_cond (Int.eq Int.zero) rs CN
  | TCmi => (* negative *)
      eval_unary_cond (Int.eq Int.one) rs CN
  end.

Definition ofs_of_size (is_32bits:bool) :=
  if is_32bits then wsize else isize.



Definition aexec_instr (is_32bits : bool) (i:instruction) (rs: aregset) (astk: astack) (b:block) (m:mem) : aoutcome :=
  match i with
  | Padd r1 r2 so =>
        match aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op so rs) with
        | None => AStuck
        | Some v => ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- v)) astk b m
        end
  | Pand r1 r2 so => (* and_imm/reg: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.and rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op so rs)))) astk b m
  | Pasr r1 r2 r3 => (* asr_reg: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.shr rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pb lbl =>
      agoto_label lbl rs b astk m
  | Pbc cond lbl =>
      match aeval_testcond cond rs with
      | Some true => agoto_label lbl rs b astk m
      | Some false => ANext (anextinstr is_32bits rs) astk b m
      | None => AStuck
      end
  | Pbreg r => (* BX reg is 16-bit *)
      ANext (rs#PC <- (rs#r)) astk b m
  | Pblreg r =>
      ANext (rs#IR14 <- (aoffset_ptr rs#PC (size_of_bool is_32bits)) #PC <- (rs#r)) astk b m
  | Pbic r1 r2 so =>
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.and rs#r2 (alift1 Val.notint (aeval_shift_op so rs))))) astk b m
  | Pcmp r1 so =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (acompare_int rs rs#r1 (aeval_shift_op so rs) m)) astk b m

  | Pcmn r1 so =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (acompare_int rs rs#r1 (alift1 Val.neg (aeval_shift_op so rs)) m)) astk b m
  | Peor r1 r2 so => (* eor_imm/reg: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.xor rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op so rs)))) astk b m
  | Pldr r1 r2 sa => (* ldr_imm/reg: 32-bit *)
      aexec_load is_32bits Mint32 (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pldr_a r1 r2 sa =>
      aexec_load is_32bits Many32 (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pldrb r1 r2 sa =>
      aexec_load is_32bits Mint8unsigned (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pldrh r1 r2 sa =>
      aexec_load is_32bits Mint16unsigned (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pldrsb r1 r2 sa =>
      aexec_load is_32bits Mint8signed (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pldrsh r1 r2 sa =>
      aexec_load is_32bits Mint16signed (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Plsl r1 r2 r3 => (* lsl_reg: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.shl rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Plsr r1 r2 r3 => (* lsr_reg: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.shru rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pmla r1 r2 r3 r4 =>
      match (aadd (alift2 Val.mul rs#r2 rs#r3) rs#r4) with
      | Some v =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- v)) astk b m
      | None => AStuck
      end
  | Pmov r1 so =>
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (aeval_shift_op so rs))) astk b m
  | Pmovw r n => (* movw: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r <- (Cval (Vint n)))) astk b m
  | Pmovt r n => (* movt: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r <- (alift2 Val.or (alift2 Val.and rs#r (Cval (Vint (Int.repr 65535))))
                                       (Cval (Vint (Int.shl n (Int.repr 16))))))) astk b m
  | Pmul r1 r2 r3 => (* mul_reg: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.mul rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pmvn r1 so =>
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift1 Val.notint (aeval_shift_op so rs)))) astk b m
  | Porr r1 r2 so => (* orr_imm/reg: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.or rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op so rs)))) astk b m
  | Prsb r1 r2 so => (* rsb_imm/reg: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.sub (aeval_shift_op so rs) rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Pstr r1 r2 sa => (* str_imm/reg: 32-bit *)
      aexec_store is_32bits Mint32 (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pstr_a r1 r2 sa =>
      aexec_store is_32bits Many32 (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pstrb r1 r2 sa =>
      aexec_store is_32bits Mint8unsigned (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pstrh r1 r2 sa =>
      aexec_store is_32bits Mint16unsigned (aadd rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op sa rs)) r1 rs astk b m
  | Psdiv =>
      match adivs rs#IR0 rs#IR1 with
      | Some v => ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#IR0 <- v
                                     #IR1 <- (Cval Vundef) #IR2 <- (Cval Vundef)
                                     #IR3 <- (Cval Vundef) #IR12 <- (Cval Vundef))) astk b m
      | None => AStuck
      end
  | Psbfx r1 r2 lsb sz =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift1 (Val.sign_ext (Int.unsigned sz)) (alift2 Val.shru rs#r2 (Cval (Vint lsb)))))) astk b m
  | Psmull rdl rdh r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#rdl <- (alift2 Val.mul rs#r1 rs#r2)
                         #rdh <- (alift2 Val.mulhs rs#r1 rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Psub r1 r2 so => (* sub_imm/reg: 32-bit *)
      ANext (anextinstr_nf is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.sub rs#r2 (aeval_shift_op so rs)))) astk b m
  | Pudiv => (* udiv r0, r1, r0 : 32-bit *)
      match adivu rs#IR0 rs#IR1 with
      | Some v => ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#IR0 <- v
                                     #IR1 <- (Cval Vundef) #IR2 <- (Cval Vundef)
                                     #IR3 <- (Cval Vundef) #IR12 <- (Cval Vundef))) astk b m
      | None => AStuck
      end
  | Pumull rdl rdh r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#rdl <- (alift2 Val.mul rs#r1 rs#r2)
                         #rdh <- (alift2 Val.mulhu rs#r1 rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Pfcpyd r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Pfabsd r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift1 Val.absf rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Pfnegd r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift1 Val.negf rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Pfaddd r1 r2 r3 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.addf rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pfdivd r1 r2 r3 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.divf rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pfmuld r1 r2 r3 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.mulf rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pfsubd r1 r2 r3 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.subf rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pflid r1 f =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#IR14 <- (Cval Vundef) #r1 <- (Cval (Vfloat f)))) astk b m
  | Pfcmpd r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (acompare_float rs rs#r1 rs#r2)) astk b m
  | Pfcmpzd r1 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (acompare_float rs rs#r1 (Cval (Vfloat Float.zero)))) astk b m
  | Pfsitod r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (amaketotal (alifto1 Val.floatofint rs#r2)))) astk b m
  | Pfuitod r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (amaketotal (alifto1 Val.floatofintu rs#r2)))) astk b m
  | Pftosizd r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs #FR6 <- (Cval Vundef) #r1 <- (amaketotal (alifto1 Val.intoffloat rs#r2)))) astk b m
  | Pftouizd r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs #FR6 <- (Cval Vundef) #r1 <- (amaketotal (alifto1 Val.intuoffloat rs#r2)))) astk b m
  | Pfabss r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift1 Val.absfs rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Pfnegs r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift1 Val.negfs rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Pfadds r1 r2 r3 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.addfs rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pfdivs r1 r2 r3 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.divfs rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pfmuls r1 r2 r3 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.mulfs rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pfsubs r1 r2 r3 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift2 Val.subfs rs#r2 rs#r3))) astk b m
  | Pflis r1 f =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (Cval (Vsingle f)))) astk b m
  | Pfcmps r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (acompare_float32 rs rs#r1 rs#r2)) astk b m
  | Pfcmpzs r1 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (acompare_float32 rs rs#r1 (Cval (Vsingle Float32.zero)))) astk b m
  | Pfsitos r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (amaketotal (alifto1 Val.singleofint rs#r2)))) astk b m
  | Pfuitos r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (amaketotal (alifto1 Val.singleofintu rs#r2)))) astk b m
  | Pftosizs r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs #FR6 <- (Cval Vundef) #r1 <- (amaketotal (alifto1 Val.intofsingle rs#r2)))) astk b m
  | Pftouizs r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs #FR6 <- (Cval Vundef) #r1 <- (amaketotal (alifto1 Val.intuofsingle rs#r2)))) astk b m
  | Pfcvtsd r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift1 Val.singleoffloat rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Pfcvtds r1 r2 =>
      ANext (anextinstr is_32bits (rs#r1 <- (alift1 Val.floatofsingle rs#r2))) astk b m
  | Pfldd r1 r2 n =>
      aexec_load is_32bits Mfloat64 (aadd rs#r2 (Cval (Vint n))) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pfldd_a r1 r2 n =>
      aexec_load is_32bits Many64 (aadd rs#r2 (Cval (Vint n))) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pflds r1 r2 n =>
      aexec_load is_32bits Mfloat32 (aadd rs#r2 (Cval (Vint n))) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pfstd r1 r2 n =>
      aexec_store is_32bits Mfloat64 (aadd rs#r2 (Cval (Vint n))) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pfstd_a r1 r2 n =>
      aexec_store is_32bits Many64 (aadd rs#r2 (Cval (Vint n))) r1 rs astk b m
  | Pfsts r1 r2 n =>
      aexec_store is_32bits Mfloat32 (aadd rs#r2 (Cval (Vint n))) r1 rs astk b m
  end.


Fixpoint map_filter [A B:Type] (f :A -> option B) (l : list A) : option (list B) :=
  match l with
  | nil => Some nil
  | e::l => match f e with
            | None => None
            | Some e' => match map_filter f l with
                         | None => None
                         | Some l' => Some (e'::l')
                         end
            end
  end.

Definition mach_param_regs := (R0 :: R1 :: R2 :: R3 :: nil).


Fixpoint alloc_arguments (lv:list val) (lt:list typ) (lr:list mreg) : option (list (preg * val)) :=
  match lv,lt,lr with
  | nil , nil , _ => Some nil
  | v1::lv1 , Tint ::lt1 , r1 ::lr1 =>
      match alloc_arguments lv1 lt1 lr1 with
      | None => None
      | Some l => Some ((preg_of r1,v1)::l)
      end
  | _ , _ , _ => None
  end.

Definition regset0 : aregset :=
  fun r => Aval (Rval (Sreg r)).

Definition allocframe (sz: Z) (pos: ptrofs) (m:mem) (rs: aregset) :=
  let (m1,stkb) := Mem.alloc m 0 sz in
  let sp := Aval (Sval Ssp Ptrofs.zero) in
  let stk := (ZMap.init (Cmemval Undef)) in
  match astack_store Mint32 m1 stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned pos) (rs IR13) with
  | None => AStuck
  | Some stk' => ANext (incrinstr (rs #IR12 <- (rs#IR13) #IR13 <- sp)) stk' stkb m1
  end.


init_state models argument passing and initialise a stack frame
Definition init_state (s:signature) (sz:Z) (pos:ptrofs) (l:list val) (m:mem) : aoutcome :=
  match alloc_arguments l (sig_args s) int_param_regs with
  | None => AStuck
  | Some l =>
      let rs := init_regset l regset0 in
      match allocframe sz pos m rs with
      | AStuck => AStuck
      | ANext rs' stk' stkb' m1' =>
          ANext (rs'# IR14 <- (Aval (Sval (Sreg PC) (Ptrofs.repr 2)))
                                #PC <- (rs # IR0)) stk' stkb' m1'
      end
  end.


is_final_state holds if - PC holds the return address RA - all callee save have their value restored - Note there is no freeframe...
Definition is_final_state (rs:aregset) :=
The current PC is the value of the initial return address
  aval_eq (rs PC) (Aval (Sval (Sreg PC) (Ptrofs.repr 2)))
  &&
    aval_eq (rs SP) (Aval (Rval (Sreg SP)))
  &&
All the callee-save are restored
    List.forallb (fun r => aval_eq (rs (preg_of r)) (Aval (Rval (Sreg (preg_of r))))) (int_callee_save_regs ++ float_callee_save_regs).

Definition has_rettypeb (v:val) (r: rettype) : bool :=
  match r with
| Tret t => Val.has_type_dec v t
| Tint8signed => match v with
                 | Vundef => true
                 | Vint n => Int.eq n (Int.sign_ext 8 n)
                 | _ => false
                 end
| Tint8unsigned => match v with
                   | Vundef => true
                   | Vint n => Int.eq n (Int.zero_ext 8 n)
                   | _ => false
                   end
| Tint16signed => match v with
                  | Vundef => true
                  | Vint n => Int.eq n (Int.sign_ext 16 n)
                  | _ => false
                  end
| Tint16unsigned => match v with
                    | Vundef => true
                    | Vint n => Int.eq n (Int.zero_ext 16 n)
                    | _ => false
                    end
| Tvoid => match v with
           | Vundef => true
           | _ => false
           end
end.

Definition has_rettypeb_iff : forall (v:val) (r: rettype),
    Val.has_rettype v r <-> has_rettypeb v r = true.
Proof.
  unfold Val.has_rettype, has_rettypeb.
  destruct r; simpl; try (intuition congruence).
  - destruct (Val.has_type_dec v t).
    simpl. intuition congruence.
    simpl. intuition congruence.
  - destruct v ; simpl; try intuition congruence.
    generalize (Int.eq_spec i (Int.sign_ext 8 i)).
    destruct (Int.eq i (Int.sign_ext 8 i)).
    intuition congruence.
    intuition congruence.
  - destruct v ; simpl; try intuition congruence.
    generalize (Int.eq_spec i (Int.zero_ext 8 i)).
    destruct (Int.eq i (Int.zero_ext 8 i)).
    intuition congruence.
    intuition congruence.
  - destruct v ; simpl; try intuition congruence.
    generalize (Int.eq_spec i (Int.sign_ext 16 i)).
    destruct (Int.eq i (Int.sign_ext 16 i)).
    intuition congruence.
    intuition congruence.
  - destruct v ; simpl; try intuition congruence.
    generalize (Int.eq_spec i (Int.zero_ext 16 i)).
    destruct (Int.eq i (Int.zero_ext 16 i)).
    intuition congruence.
    intuition congruence.
  - destruct v ; simpl; try intuition congruence.
Qed.

Definition is_definedb (v:val) : bool :=
  match v with
  | Vundef => false
  | _ => true
  end.

Lemma is_defined_inv : forall v, is_definedb v = true <-> v <> Vundef.
Proof.
  destruct v ; simpl; intuition try congruence.
Qed.

Definition get_result (r:rettype) (v:aval) (m:mem) : option (val * mem) :=
  match v with
  | Cval v => if is_definedb v && has_rettypeb v r then Some (v,m) else None
  | _ => None
  end.

Fixpoint bin_interp (rt:rettype) (n:nat) (rs: aregset) (stk : astack) (stkb: block) (m : mem) : option (val*mem) :=
  if is_final_state rs
  then get_result rt (rs IR0) m
  else
    match n with
    | O => None
    | Datatypes.S n =>
        match find_instr (rs # PC) m with
        | None => None
        | Some (i,sz) =>
            match aexec_instr sz i rs stk stkb m with
            | ANext rs' stk' stkb m' => bin_interp rt n rs' stk' stkb m'
            | AStuck => None
            end
        end
    end.


Definition bin_exec (n:nat) (s:signature) (sz:Z) (pos:ptrofs) (args: list val) (m : mem) : option (val*mem) :=
  match init_state s sz pos args m with
  | ANext rs stk stkb m1 => bin_interp (sig_res s) n rs stk stkb m1
  | AStuck => None
  end.


Section S.
  Variables trace : Type.
  Variables E0 : trace.

  Record bin_exec_sem (n:nat) (s:signature) (sz:Z) (pos: ptrofs) (e:Senv.t) (l:list val) (m:mem) (t:trace) (r:val) (m':mem) : Prop :=
    mk_bin_exec {
      no_trace : t = E0;
      has_exec : bin_exec n s sz pos l m = Some (r,m')
    }.

Lemma get_result_inv_mem :
  forall rt v m r m',
    get_result rt v m = Some (r, m') -> m = m'.
Proof.
  unfold get_result.
  destruct v. intros.
  destruct (is_definedb v && has_rettypeb v rt); congruence.
  discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma get_result_rettype :
  forall rt r m vres m'
         (GET : get_result rt r m = Some (vres, m')),
  Val.has_rettype vres rt.
Proof.
  unfold get_result.
  destruct r ; try discriminate.
  intros.
  rewrite has_rettypeb_iff.
  destruct (is_definedb v && has_rettypeb v rt) eqn:RT; try congruence.
  rewrite andb_true_iff in RT. intuition congruence.
Qed.


Lemma aexec_load_nextblock :
  forall is_32bits chunk a i rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m',
    aexec_load is_32bits chunk a i rs
         stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m' ->
  Mem.nextblock m = Mem.nextblock m'.
Proof.
  unfold aexec_load.
  destruct a; intros.
  destruct a.
  - destruct (Mem.loadv chunk m v) eqn:LOAD; try discriminate.
    inv H. reflexivity.
  -
    destruct (get_stack_offset v) eqn:GSO; try discriminate.
    destruct (astack_load chunk m stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i0)); try discriminate.
    inv H; auto.
  - discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_store_nextblock :
  forall is_32bits chunk a r rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m',
    aexec_store is_32bits chunk a r rs
         stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m' ->
  Mem.nextblock m = Mem.nextblock m'.
Proof.
  unfold aexec_store,aexec_store'.
  destruct a; intros; try discriminate.
  destruct (is_stack_pointer stkb a) eqn:ISP; try discriminate.
  - destruct (astack_store chunk m stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i) (rs r)) ; try discriminate.
    inv H. reflexivity.
  -
  destruct a; try discriminate.
  + destruct (rs r) ; try discriminate.
    destruct_in H eq: STK ; try discriminate.
    destruct_in STK eq: STK1 ; try discriminate.
    destruct (Mem.storev chunk m v v0) eqn: STORE; try discriminate.
    inv H. inv STK.
    unfold Mem.storev in STORE.
    destruct v ; try discriminate.
    apply Mem.nextblock_store in STORE;auto.
    congruence.
Qed.

Lemma agoto_label_inv_mem :
  forall i rs stkb stk m rs' stk' stkb' m',
    agoto_label i rs stkb stk m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m' ->
    m = m'.
Proof.
  unfold agoto_label.
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_instr_nextblock :
  forall w i rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m'
    (EXEC : aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m'),
  Mem.nextblock m = Mem.nextblock m'.
Proof.
  destruct i eqn:I; simpl ; intros; try congruence;
    try (eapply aexec_load_nextblock in EXEC ; congruence);
    try (eapply aexec_store_nextblock in EXEC ; congruence).
  -
    destruct (aadd (rs i1) (aeval_shift_op s rs)); try discriminate.
    congruence.
  - intros.
    apply agoto_label_inv_mem in EXEC; congruence.
  - intros.
    destruct (aeval_testcond t rs); try congruence.
    destruct b.
    apply agoto_label_inv_mem in EXEC; congruence.
    congruence.
  - destruct (aadd (alift2 Val.mul (rs i1) (rs i2)) (rs i3)); congruence.
  - destruct (adivs (rs IR0) (rs IR1)); congruence.
  - destruct (adivu (rs IR0) (rs IR1)); congruence.
Qed.

Lemma bin_exec_sem_next_block :
  forall n s sz pos ge vargs m1 t vres m2,
    bin_exec_sem n s sz pos ge vargs m1 t vres m2 ->
    (Mem.nextblock m1 + 1 = Mem.nextblock m2)%positive.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct H.
  unfold bin_exec in has_exec0.
  destruct (init_state s sz pos vargs m1) eqn:I1; try discriminate.
  assert (NEXTINIT : (Mem.nextblock m = Mem.nextblock m1 + 1)%positive).
  { unfold init_state in I1. clear has_exec0.
    destruct (alloc_arguments vargs (sig_args s) int_param_regs).
    - destruct_in I1 eq:AF;
        try discriminate.
      inv I1.
      unfold allocframe in AF.
      destruct (Mem.alloc m1 0 sz) eqn:MA.
      apply Mem.nextblock_alloc in MA.
      destruct_in AF eq:_AF ; try discriminate.
      inv AF.
      lia.
    - discriminate.
  }
  rewrite <- NEXTINIT.
  clear - has_exec0.
  rename a into rs.
  rename a0 into stk.
  rename b into stkb.
  revert rs stk stkb m vres m2 has_exec0.
  induction n.
  - simpl.
    intros. destruct (is_final_state rs).
    apply get_result_inv_mem in has_exec0.
    congruence.
    discriminate.
  - simpl.
    intros.
    destruct (is_final_state rs) ; try discriminate.
    apply get_result_inv_mem in has_exec0.
    congruence.
    destruct (find_instr (rs PC) m); try discriminate.
    destruct p as (i,sz).
    destruct (aexec_instr sz i rs stk stkb m) eqn:AI; try discriminate.
    apply IHn in has_exec0.
    rewrite <- has_exec0.
    apply aexec_instr_nextblock in AI.
    congruence.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_load_perms :
  forall w chunk addr r rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m' b ofs p
         (EX1 : aexec_load w chunk addr r
          rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m')
         (PERM : Mem.perm m' b ofs Max p),
  Mem.perm m b ofs Max p.
Proof.
  unfold aexec_load.
  intros. destruct addr; try discriminate.
  destruct a.
  - destruct (Mem.loadv chunk m v); congruence.
  -
    destruct (get_stack_offset v); try congruence.
    destruct (astack_load chunk m stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i)); congruence.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_store_perms :
  forall w chunk addr r rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m' b ofs p
         (EX1 : aexec_store w chunk addr r
          rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m')
         (PERM : Mem.perm m' b ofs Max p),
  Mem.perm m b ofs Max p.
Proof.
  unfold aexec_store,aexec_store'.
  intros. destruct addr; try discriminate.
  destruct (is_stack_pointer stkb a) eqn:ISP; try discriminate.
  - destruct (astack_store chunk m stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i) (rs r)); try discriminate.
    inv EX1. auto.
  -
    destruct a; try discriminate.
    destruct (rs r); try discriminate.
    destruct_in EX1 eq:M; try discriminate.
    destruct_in M eq:ISP1;try discriminate.
    destruct (Mem.storev chunk m v v0) eqn:STORE;try discriminate.
    inv EX1. inv M. inv ISP1.
    unfold Mem.storev in STORE.
    destruct v ; try discriminate.
    eapply Mem.perm_store_2; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_instr_perm :
  forall w i rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m' b ofs p
         (EX1 : aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m')
         (PERM : Mem.perm m' b ofs Max p),
  Mem.perm m b ofs Max p.
Proof.
  destruct i; intros; simpl in EX1; try congruence;
    try (eapply aexec_load_perms; eauto;fail);
    try (eapply aexec_store_perms; eauto;fail).
  - destruct (aadd (rs i0) (aeval_shift_op s rs)); congruence.
  - unfold agoto_label in EX1. congruence.
  - destruct (aeval_testcond t rs); try congruence.
    destruct b0 ; simpl; try congruence.
    unfold agoto_label in EX1. congruence.
  - destruct (aadd (alift2 Val.mul (rs i0) (rs i1)) (rs i2)); congruence.
  - destruct (adivs (rs IR0) (rs IR1)); try congruence.
  - destruct (adivu (rs IR0) (rs IR1)); try congruence.
Qed.

Lemma bin_interp_same_perm :
  forall rt n rs stk stkb m vres m' b ofs p
         (EX : bin_interp rt n rs stk stkb m = Some (vres, m'))
         (PERM : Mem.perm m' b ofs Max p),
  Mem.perm m b ofs Max p.
Proof.
  induction n.
  - simpl. intros.
    destruct (is_final_state rs); try discriminate.
    apply get_result_inv_mem in EX. congruence.
  - intros.
    simpl in EX.
    destruct (is_final_state rs); try discriminate.
    apply get_result_inv_mem in EX. congruence.
    destruct (find_instr (rs PC) m) as [(i& w)|]; try discriminate.
    destruct (aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m) eqn:EX1;try discriminate.
    eapply IHn in EX;eauto.
    eapply aexec_instr_perm ; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma allocframe_mem : forall sz pos m rs,
    allocframe sz pos m rs <> AStuck ->
  exists rs' stk',
    allocframe sz pos m rs =
    let (m1,stkb) := Mem.alloc m 0 sz in
    ANext rs' stk' stkb m1.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold allocframe in *.
  destruct (Mem.alloc m 0 sz) as (m1,stkb).
  simpl in *.
  destruct_in H eq:_E.
  do 2 eexists; reflexivity.
  congruence.
Qed.



Lemma init_state_perm :
  forall s sz pos vargs m1 rs stk stkb m b ofs p
  (I : init_state s sz pos vargs m1 = ANext rs stk stkb m)
  (VALID : Mem.valid_block m1 b)
  (PERM : Mem.perm m b ofs Max p),
  Mem.perm m1 b ofs Max p.
Proof.
  unfold init_state.
  intros.
  destruct (alloc_arguments vargs (sig_args s) int_param_regs);
    try discriminate.
  destruct_in I eq:AF; try discriminate.
  inv I.
  exploit allocframe_mem.
  rewrite AF. congruence.
  intros (rs' & stk' & M).
  rewrite AF in M.
  destruct (Mem.alloc m1 0 sz) eqn:ALLOC.
  inv M.
  assert (ALLOC' := ALLOC).
  eapply Mem.perm_alloc_inv with (b':= b) (ofs:= ofs)
                                 (k:= Max) (p:=p)
    in ALLOC; eauto.
  - destruct (eq_block b b0); auto.
    subst ; auto.
    apply Mem.fresh_block_alloc in ALLOC'.
    tauto.
Qed.

Lemma bin_exec_sem_perm :
  forall n s sz pos ge vargs m1 t vres m2 b ofs p
    (EXEC : bin_exec_sem n s sz pos ge vargs m1 t vres m2)
    (VALID : Mem.valid_block m1 b)
    (PERM : Mem.perm m2 b ofs Max p),
  Mem.perm m1 b ofs Max p.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct EXEC.
  unfold bin_exec in has_exec0.
  destruct (init_state s sz pos vargs m1) eqn:I ; try discriminate.
  eapply bin_interp_same_perm in has_exec0;eauto.
  eapply init_state_perm; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma init_state_load_bytes :
  forall s sz pos vargs m1 rs stk stkb m b ofs n bytes
         (I : init_state s sz pos vargs m1 = ANext rs stk stkb m)
         (VALID : Mem.valid_block m1 b)
         (LOAD : Mem.loadbytes m b ofs n = Some bytes)
         (RO : forall i : Z, ofs <= i < ofs + n -> ~ Mem.perm m1 b i Max Writable),
    Mem.loadbytes m1 b ofs n = Some bytes.
Proof.
  unfold init_state.
  intros.
  destruct (alloc_arguments vargs (sig_args s) int_param_regs) ; try discriminate.
  destruct_in I eq:AF ;
    try discriminate.
  exploit allocframe_mem;eauto.
  rewrite AF. discriminate.
  intros (rs' & stk' & ALL).
  destruct (Mem.alloc m1 0 sz) eqn:ALLOC; try discriminate.
  rewrite <- Mem.loadbytes_alloc_unchanged with (1:= ALLOC); auto.
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma init_state_valid_block :
  forall s sz pos vargs m1 rs stk stkb m2 b,
    init_state s sz pos vargs m1 = ANext rs stk stkb m2 ->
    Mem.valid_block m1 b ->
    Mem.valid_block m2 b.
Proof.
  unfold init_state.
  intros.
  destruct (alloc_arguments vargs (sig_args s) int_param_regs);
    try discriminate.
  destruct_in H eq:AF; try discriminate.
  exploit allocframe_mem ; eauto.
  rewrite AF; congruence.
  intros (rs' & stk' & ALL).
  destruct (Mem.alloc m1 0 sz) eqn: ALLOC.
  rewrite AF in ALL. inv ALL. inv H.
  eapply Mem.valid_block_alloc; eauto.
Qed.


Lemma aexec_load_inv_mem :
  forall w chunk addr r rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m'
         (EI : aexec_load w chunk addr r rs
                          stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m'),
    m = m'.
Proof.
  unfold aexec_load.
  intros. destruct addr; try congruence.
  destruct a; try congruence.
  - destruct (Mem.loadv chunk m v); congruence.
  - destruct (get_stack_offset v); try congruence.
    destruct (astack_load chunk m stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i)); congruence.
Qed.

Lemma bin_exec_rettype :
  forall n sg sz pos vargs m vres m'
         (EX: ABinSem.bin_exec n sg sz pos vargs m = Some (vres, m')),
  Val.has_rettype vres (sig_res sg).
Proof.
  unfold bin_exec.
  intros.
  destruct (init_state sg sz pos vargs m) eqn:I;try discriminate.
  revert EX.
  rename a into rs. rename a0 into stk.
  rename b into stkb.
  clear.
  revert rs stk stkb m0 vres m'.
  induction n; simpl.
  - intros.
    destruct (is_final_state rs); try discriminate.
    apply get_result_rettype in EX; auto.
  - intros.
    destruct (is_final_state rs); try discriminate.
    apply get_result_rettype in EX; auto.
    destruct (find_instr (rs PC) m0) as [(i & w)|]; try discriminate.
    destruct (aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m0); try discriminate.
    eapply IHn;eauto.
Qed.

Definition loc_readonly (m : mem) (b : block) (ofs : Z) :=
  Mem.valid_block m b /\ loc_not_writable m b ofs.

Lemma loc_readonly_not_writable : forall m m',
    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_readonly m) m m' ->
    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_not_writable m) m m'.
Proof.
  intros.
  eapply Mem.unchanged_on_implies; eauto.
  intros.
  unfold loc_readonly. tauto.
Qed.


Lemma aexec_store_unchanged_on_readonly :
  forall w chunk addr r rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m'
         (STORE : aexec_store w chunk
                              addr r rs stk stkb m
            = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m'),
  Mem.unchanged_on (loc_readonly m) m m'.
Proof.
  unfold aexec_store,aexec_store'.
  destruct addr; try congruence.
  intros.
  destruct (is_stack_pointer stkb a) eqn:ISP;try discriminate.
  - destruct_in STORE eq:STORE1;try discriminate.
    destruct_in STORE1 eq:STORE2;try discriminate.
    inv STORE1; inv STORE2;auto.
    inv STORE;auto.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  -
    destruct a; try congruence.
    + intros. destruct (rs r); try discriminate.
      destruct (Mem.storev chunk m v v0) eqn:STOREV;try discriminate.
      inv STORE. unfold Mem.storev in STOREV.
      destruct v ; try discriminate.
      eapply Mem.store_unchanged_on; eauto.
      exploit Mem.store_valid_access_3; eauto. intros [P Q].
      intros. unfold loc_not_writable. red; intros.
      unfold loc_readonly in H0.
      destruct H0 as [HH0 HH1].
      elim HH1.
      apply Mem.perm_cur_max. apply P. auto.
Qed.

Lemma init_state_unchanged_on_readonly :
  forall s sz pos vargs m1 m rs stk stkb P
         (I : init_state s sz pos vargs m1 = ANext rs stk stkb m),
  Mem.unchanged_on P m1 m.
Proof.
  unfold init_state.
  intros.
  destruct (alloc_arguments vargs (sig_args s) int_param_regs);
    try discriminate.
  destruct_in I eq:AF ; try discriminate.
  exploit allocframe_mem ; eauto.
  rewrite AF;congruence.
  intros (rs' & stk' & AF').
  rewrite AF in AF'.
  destruct (Mem.alloc m1 0 sz) eqn:ALLOC.
  inv AF'. inv I.
  eapply Mem.alloc_unchanged_on; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_store_readonly :
  forall w chunk addr r rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m'
         (EXI : aexec_store w chunk addr r rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m'),
  Mem.unchanged_on (loc_not_writable m) m m'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold aexec_store, aexec_store' in EXI.
  destruct addr; try discriminate.
  destruct (is_stack_pointer stkb a) eqn:ISP;try discriminate.
  - destruct (astack_store chunk m stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i) (rs r)); try discriminate. inv EXI.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  -
    destruct a; try congruence.
    + destruct (rs r); try discriminate.
    destruct (Mem.storev chunk m v v0) eqn:STOREV; try discriminate.
    inv EXI. unfold Mem.storev in STOREV.
    destruct v ; try discriminate.
    eapply Mem.store_unchanged_on;eauto.
    exploit Mem.store_valid_access_3; eauto. intros [P Q].
    intros. unfold loc_not_writable. red; intros. elim H0.
    apply Mem.perm_cur_max. apply P. auto.
Qed.


Lemma aexec_instr_readonly :
  forall w i rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m'
    (EXI : aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m'),
  Mem.unchanged_on (loc_not_writable m) m m'.
Proof.
  destruct i; simpl;
    try (intros; inv EXI ; apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl);
    try (intros; apply aexec_load_inv_mem in EXI; subst ;
         apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl);
    try (intros; eapply aexec_store_readonly ; eauto;fail).
  - intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i0) (aeval_shift_op s rs)); try congruence.
    inv EXI. apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  - intros.
    destruct (aeval_testcond t rs).
    + destruct b.
      apply agoto_label_inv_mem in EXI.
      subst. apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
      inv EXI. apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
    + discriminate.
  - intros.
    destruct (aadd (alift2 Val.mul (rs i0) (rs i1)) (rs i2)) ; try discriminate.
    inv EXI. apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  - intros.
    destruct (adivs (rs IR0) (rs IR1)); try discriminate.
    inv EXI. apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  - intros.
    destruct (adivu (rs IR0) (rs IR1)); try discriminate.
    inv EXI. apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
Qed.

Lemma bin_interp_readonly :
  forall rt n1 rs stk stkb m vres m2
         (EXEC : bin_interp rt n1 rs stk stkb m = Some (vres, m2)),
  Mem.unchanged_on (loc_not_writable m) m m2.
Proof.
  induction n1.
  - simpl.
    intros.
    destruct (is_final_state rs); try discriminate.
    apply get_result_inv_mem in EXEC.
    subst. apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  - simpl.
    intros.
    destruct (is_final_state rs); try discriminate.
    apply get_result_inv_mem in EXEC.
    subst. apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
    destruct (find_instr (rs PC) m) as [(i,w)|]; try discriminate.
    destruct (aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m) eqn:EXI; try discriminate.
    eapply Mem.unchanged_on_trans with (m2:=m0).
    eapply aexec_instr_readonly;eauto.
    eapply Mem.unchanged_on_implies.
    eapply IHn1 ;eauto.
    unfold loc_not_writable.
    intros. intro. apply H.
    eapply aexec_instr_perm; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma bin_exec_sem_readonly :
  forall ns s sz pos ge vargs m1 t vres m2 b ofs n bytes
         (EXEC : bin_exec_sem ns s sz pos ge vargs m1 t vres m2)
         (VALID : Mem.valid_block m1 b)
         (LOAD : Mem.loadbytes m2 b ofs n = Some bytes)
         (RO : forall i : Z,
             ofs <= i < ofs + n -> ~ Mem.perm m1 b i Max Writable),
  Mem.loadbytes m1 b ofs n = Some bytes.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct EXEC.
  eapply unchanged_on_readonly; eauto.
  unfold bin_exec in has_exec0.
  destruct (init_state s sz pos vargs m1) eqn:I; try discriminate.
  apply Mem.unchanged_on_implies with (loc_not_writable m).
  eapply Mem.unchanged_on_trans with (m2:=m).
  eapply init_state_unchanged_on_readonly;eauto.
  eapply bin_interp_readonly; eauto.
  unfold loc_not_writable.
  intros. intro. apply H.
  eapply init_state_perm;eauto.
Qed.

Lemma bin_exec_sem_rettype :
  forall n s sz pos ge vargs m1 t vres m2,
    bin_exec_sem n s sz pos ge vargs m1 t vres m2 ->
  Val.has_rettype vres (sig_res s).
Proof.
  intros. destruct H.
  eapply bin_exec_rettype;eauto.
Qed.

Inductive aval_lessdef : aval -> aval -> Prop :=
| aval_lessdef_refl : forall v, aval_lessdef v v
| aval_lessdef_val : forall v v', Val.lessdef v v' -> aval_lessdef (Cval v) (Cval v').

Hint Resolve aval_lessdef_refl : ld.

Lemma aval_lessdef_trans : forall v1 v2 v3,
    aval_lessdef v1 v2 ->
    aval_lessdef v2 v3 ->
    aval_lessdef v1 v3.
Proof.
  intros.
  inv H. auto.
  inv H0.
  constructor;auto.
  constructor.
  eapply Val.lessdef_trans;eauto.
Qed.


Definition aregset_lessdef (rs rs' : aregset) :=
  forall x, aval_lessdef (rs x) (rs' x).

Lemma alloc_arguments_lessdef :
  forall vargs vargs' args regs l
         (LD : Val.lessdef_list vargs vargs')
         (AA : alloc_arguments vargs args regs = Some l)
  ,
    exists l',
      alloc_arguments vargs' args regs = Some l'
      /\ list_forall2 (fun rv rv' => fst rv = fst rv' /\
                                       Val.lessdef (snd rv) (snd rv')) l l'.
Proof.
  intros.
  revert args regs l AA.
  induction LD.
  - simpl.
    destruct args; try discriminate.
    simpl ; intros.
    inv AA.
    exists nil.
    split ; auto.
    constructor.
  - simpl.
    destruct args ; try discriminate.
    destruct t ; try discriminate.
    destruct regs ; try discriminate.
    intros.
    destruct (alloc_arguments vl1 args regs) eqn:AA'; try discriminate.
    inv AA.
    apply IHLD in AA'.
    destruct AA' as (l' & AA2 & FA).
    rewrite AA2.
    exists ((preg_of m,v2)::l').
    split ; auto.
    constructor; auto.
Qed.

Lemma aregset_refl : forall rs,
    aregset_lessdef rs rs.
Proof.
  repeat intro.
  constructor.
Qed.


Lemma aregset_set_lessdef : forall rs rs' x v v',
    aval_lessdef v v' ->
    aregset_lessdef rs rs' ->
    aregset_lessdef (rs # x <- v) (rs' # x <- v').
Proof.
  intros.
  intro.
  destruct (preg_eq x0 x).
  - subst.
    rewrite! Pregmap.gss.
    auto.
  - rewrite! Pregmap.gso by congruence.
    auto.
Qed.

Hint Resolve aregset_set_lessdef : ld.


Lemma update_regset_lessdef :
  forall l l'
         (A_LD : list_forall2
             (fun rv rv' : preg * aval =>
                fst rv = fst rv' /\ aval_lessdef (snd rv) (snd rv')) l
             l')
         rs rs'
         (RS_LD : aregset_lessdef rs rs')
,
         aregset_lessdef (update_regset l rs) (update_regset l' rs').
Proof.
  intros l l' A_LD.
  induction A_LD.
  - simpl. auto.
  - simpl.
    intros.
    destruct a1, b1.
    simpl in *. destruct H ; subst.
    intro.
    apply aregset_set_lessdef.
    inv H0. constructor.
    constructor. auto.
    apply IHA_LD; auto.
Qed.

Lemma list_forall2_map : forall [A B C: Type] (f: A -> C) (g: B -> C)
                                (P : C -> C -> Prop) l1 l2,
    list_forall2 (fun x y => P (f x) (g y)) l1 l2 ->
    list_forall2 P (map f l1) (map g l2).
Proof.
  intros.
  induction H.
  - constructor.
  - simpl. constructor; auto.
Qed.

Lemma list_forall2_implies :
  forall [A:Type] (P Q : A -> A -> Prop) l1 l2
         (IMPL : forall x y, P x y -> Q x y),
         list_forall2 P l1 l2 ->
         list_forall2 Q l1 l2.
Proof.
  intros.
  induction H. constructor.
  constructor ; auto.
Qed.

Lemma init_regset_lessdef :
  forall l l'
         (A_LD : list_forall2
             (fun rv rv' : preg * val =>
                fst rv = fst rv' /\ Val.lessdef (snd rv) (snd rv')) l
             l')
         rs rs'
         (RS_LD : aregset_lessdef rs rs')
,
         aregset_lessdef (init_regset l rs) (init_regset l' rs').
Proof.
  intros l l' A_LD.
  intros.
  unfold init_regset.
  apply update_regset_lessdef; auto.
  apply list_forall2_map.
  eapply list_forall2_implies; eauto.
  simpl. destruct x,y; simpl.
  intuition subst. constructor. auto.
Qed.


Definition is_undef (v : memval) :=
  match v with
  | Undef | Fragment Vundef _ _ => true
  | _ => false
  end.

Inductive amemval_lessdef : amemval -> amemval -> Prop :=
| Amemval_lessdef : forall v, amemval_lessdef v v
| Amemval_memval : forall v v',
    memval_lessdef v v' ->
    amemval_lessdef (Cmemval v) (Cmemval v').

Definition astack_lessdef (s s': astack) :=
  forall i, amemval_lessdef (ZMap.get i s) (ZMap.get i s').

Lemma list_forall2_refl :
  forall [A: Type] (P:A -> A -> Prop) (l: list A)
         (Prefl : forall (x:A), P x x),
  list_forall2 P l l.
Proof.
  induction l.
  - constructor.
  - constructor ; auto.
Qed.

Lemma list_forall2_refl' :
  forall [A: Type] (P:A -> A -> Prop) (l: list A)
         (Prefl : forall (x:A), In x l -> P x x),
  list_forall2 P l l.
Proof.
  induction l.
  - constructor.
  - constructor ; auto.
    apply Prefl. simpl. tauto.
    apply IHl;auto.
    intros. apply Prefl. simpl. tauto.
Qed.



Lemma amemval_lessdef_refl :
  forall x : amemval, amemval_lessdef x x.
Proof.
  intros. constructor.
Qed.


Lemma encode_val_Undef_lessdef :
  forall l n
         (LEN : length l = n),
         list_forall2 memval_lessdef (repeat Undef n) l.
Proof.
  induction l.
  - simpl. intros. subst.
    constructor.
  - simpl.
    destruct n. lia.
    simpl. constructor.
    constructor.
    apply IHl. lia.
Qed.

Lemma inj_value_lessdef : forall q v v',
    Val.lessdef v v' ->
    list_forall2 memval_lessdef (inj_value q v)
    (inj_value q v').
Proof.
  intros.
  inv H.
  - apply list_forall2_refl.
     apply memval_lessdef_refl.
  - unfold inj_value.
    induction (size_quantity_nat q).
    + simpl. constructor.
    + simpl.
      constructor; auto.
      constructor.
      constructor.
Qed.


Lemma encode_val_lessdef : forall chunk v v',
    Val.lessdef v v' ->
    list_forall2 memval_lessdef (encode_val chunk v) (encode_val chunk v').
Proof.
  intros.
  inv H.
  apply list_forall2_refl.
  apply memval_lessdef_refl.
  simpl.
  destruct chunk; try apply encode_val_Undef_lessdef;
    rewrite? encode_val_length; auto.
  -
    assert (encode_val Many32 v' = inj_value Q32 v').
    { destruct v' ; reflexivity. }
    rewrite H.
    apply inj_value_lessdef.
    constructor.
  - assert (encode_val Many64 v' = inj_value Q64 v').
    { destruct v' ; reflexivity. }
    rewrite H.
    apply inj_value_lessdef.
    constructor.
Qed.


Lemma encode_aval_lessdef :
  forall chunk v1 v2
    (LD:aval_lessdef v1 v2),
    option_rel (list_forall2
                  amemval_lessdef) (encode_aval chunk v1) (encode_aval chunk v2).
Proof.
  intros. inv LD.
  - destruct (encode_aval chunk v2).
    + constructor.
    apply list_forall2_refl.
    apply amemval_lessdef_refl.
    + constructor.
  - simpl.
    constructor.
    unfold encode_aval.
    apply list_forall2_map.
    exploit encode_val_lessdef; eauto.
    apply list_forall2_implies.
    intros.
    constructor ; auto.
Qed.


Lemma astack_lessdef_set : forall n v1 stk1 v2 stk2,
    astack_lessdef stk1 stk2 ->
    amemval_lessdef v1 v2 ->
    astack_lessdef (ZMap.set n v1 stk1) (ZMap.set n v2 stk2).
Proof.
  repeat intro.
  rewrite !ZMap.gsspec.
  destruct (ZIndexed.eq i n). auto.
  apply H.
Qed.


Lemma astack_lessdef_setN : forall l1 l2 n stk1 stk2 ,
    astack_lessdef stk1 stk2 ->
    list_forall2 amemval_lessdef l1 l2 ->
    astack_lessdef (setN l1 n stk1) (setN l2 n stk2).
Proof.
  intros.
  revert stk1 stk2 n H.
  induction H0.
  - simpl. auto.
  - simpl.
    intros.

Lemma astack_store_lessdef :
  forall chunk m1 m2 stk1 stkb v1 v2 x stk1' stk2
         (MEXT : Mem.extends m1 m2)
         (STORE: astack_store chunk m1 stk1 stkb x v1 = Some stk1')
         (ASTKLD : astack_lessdef stk1 stk2)
         (AVALLD : aval_lessdef v1 v2),
         exists stk2',
           astack_store chunk m2 stk2 stkb x v2 = Some stk2'
           /\
             astack_lessdef stk1' stk2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold astack_store in *.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m1 chunk stkb x Writable);
    try discriminate.
  exploit Mem.valid_access_extends; eauto.
  intro ACC.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m2 chunk stkb x Writable); try tauto.
  generalize (encode_aval_lessdef chunk v1 v2 AVALLD).
  intro EC. inv EC.
  - rewrite <- H0 in STORE. discriminate.
  - rewrite <- H in STORE.
    inv STORE.
  eexists.
  split. reflexivity.
  apply astack_lessdef_setN; auto.
Qed.

Definition loc_out_of_bounds' (m : mem) (b : block) (ofs : Z) :=

Lemma allocframe_extends :
  forall sz pos m1 rs rs' stk stkb m m1' rs2
         (I : allocframe sz pos m1 rs = ANext rs2 stk stkb m)
         (ALD : aregset_lessdef rs rs')
         (EXTEND : Mem.extends m1 m1'),
  exists (rs2' : aregset) (stk': astack) (m' : mem),
    allocframe sz pos m1' rs' = ANext rs2' stk' stkb m' /\
      Mem.extends m m' /\
      aregset_lessdef rs2 rs2' /\
      astack_lessdef stk stk' /\
      Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_bounds' m1) m1' m'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold allocframe in I.
  destruct (Mem.alloc m1 0 sz) eqn:A.
  destruct_in I eq:STORE; try discriminate.
  inv I.
  unfold allocframe.
  apply Mem.alloc_extends with (m2:=m1') (lo2 := 0) (hi2 := sz) in A.
  destruct A as (m2' & A' & EXT).
  rewrite A'.
  apply astack_store_lessdef with (m2:= m2') (v2:= (rs' IR13))
                                  (stk2 := (ZMap.init (Cmemval Undef)))
    in STORE; eauto.
  destruct STORE as (stk2' & STORE & LD).
  rewrite STORE.
  do 3 eexists. split_and; auto.
  auto with ld.
  eapply Mem.alloc_unchanged_on;eauto.
  apply astack_lessdef_refl.
  auto.
  lia. lia.
Qed.

Lemma init_state_extends :
  forall s sz pos vargs vargs' m1 m1' rs stk stkb m
         (I : init_state s sz pos vargs m1 = ANext rs stk stkb m)
         (EXTEND : Mem.extends m1 m1')
         (LD : Val.lessdef_list vargs vargs'),
    exists rs' stk' m',
      init_state s sz pos vargs' m1' = ANext rs' stk' stkb m' /\
        Mem.extends m m' /\
        aregset_lessdef rs rs' /\
        astack_lessdef stk stk' /\
        Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_bounds' m1) m1' m'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold init_state in *.
  destruct (alloc_arguments vargs (sig_args s) int_param_regs)
           eqn:AA; try discriminate.
  apply alloc_arguments_lessdef with (1:=LD) in AA.
  destruct AA as (l1 & AA1 & ALL).
  rewrite AA1.
  destruct_in I eq:AF ; try discriminate.
  inv I.
  exploit allocframe_extends; eauto.
  apply init_regset_lessdef; eauto.
  apply aregset_lessdef_refl.
  intros (rs2' & stk' & m' & AF1 & ME & ARL & ASL & MU).
  rewrite AF1.
  do 3 eexists ; split_and; eauto.
  apply aregset_set_lessdef; auto.
  apply init_regset_lessdef; eauto.
  apply aregset_lessdef_refl.
  apply aregset_set_lessdef; auto.
  constructor.
Qed.

Lemma aval_eq_true: forall x y,
    aval_eq x y = true -> x = y.
Proof.
  destruct x; destruct y; simpl; try congruence.
  destruct (Val.eq v v0); simpl; congruence.
  unfold sval_eq.
  destruct v,v0; try congruence.
  rewrite andb_true_iff.
  destruct (Ptrofs.eq ofs ofs0) eqn: IEQ; try intuition congruence.
  apply Ptrofs.same_if_eq in IEQ.
  unfold sreg_eq. destruct base,base0; intuition try congruence.
  destruct (preg_eq p p0); simpl in *; intuition congruence.
  unfold sreg_eq. destruct base,base0; intuition try congruence.
  destruct (preg_eq p p0); simpl in *; intuition congruence.
Qed.





Lemma aval_eq_refl: forall x,
    aval_eq x x = true.
Proof.
  destruct x; simpl; try congruence.
  destruct (Val.eq v v); simpl ; congruence.
  unfold sval_eq.
  destruct v; try congruence.
  rewrite andb_true_iff.
  generalize (Ptrofs.eq_spec ofs ofs).
  destruct (Ptrofs.eq ofs ofs) ; try intuition congruence.
  unfold sreg_eq. destruct base; intuition try congruence.
  destruct (preg_eq p p); simpl in *; intuition congruence.
  unfold sreg_eq. destruct base; intuition try congruence.
  destruct (preg_eq p p). reflexivity.
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma forallb_eq : forall [A: Type] (P Q: A -> bool) l,
  (forall x, P x = Q x) ->
    forallb P l = forallb Q l.

  induction l; simpl; auto.
  intros.
  rewrite IHl; auto.
  rewrite H. reflexivity.
Qed.

    exploit Mem.loadv_extends;eauto.
    intros (v3 & LOAD3 & LD3).
    rewrite LOAD3.
    inv LD3. congruence.
  - destruct (Mem.loadv Mint16unsigned m v0) eqn:LV ; try discriminate.
    destruct v ; try discriminate.
    exploit Mem.loadv_extends;eauto.
    intros (v2 & LOAD & LD).
    rewrite LOAD. inv LD.
    destruct (is_thumb2 i0); auto.
    destruct_in H eq:LV1 ; try discriminate.
    destruct v; try discriminate.
    exploit Mem.loadv_extends;eauto.
    intros (v3 & LOAD3 & LD3).
    inv LD3.
    assert (v0 = v'0).
    { inv H2; auto.
      simpl in LOAD3. discriminate.
    } subst.
    rewrite LOAD3.
    auto.
Qed.

Lemma aadd_commut : forall x y,
    aadd x y = aadd y x.
Proof.
  unfold aadd.
  destruct x,y; try reflexivity.
  destruct v,v0; try reflexivity.
  rewrite Val.add_commut. reflexivity.
  destruct v, v0; try reflexivity.
  destruct v,v0; reflexivity.
  destruct v, v0 ; try reflexivity.
Qed.

Lemma aval_lessdef_aadd :
  forall v1 v2 v1' v2' r
         (LD1 : aval_lessdef v1 v1')
         (LD2 : aval_lessdef v2 v2')
         (ADD : aadd v1 v2 = Some r),
    exists r', (aadd v1' v2') = Some r' /\ aval_lessdef r r'.
Proof.
  intros.
  assert (ADDR :
           forall v1' v v'
                  (ADD : aadd v1' (Cval v) = Some r)
                  (LD : Val.lessdef v v'),
           exists r' : aval, aadd v1' (Cval v') = Some r' /\ aval_lessdef r r').
  {
    clear.
    intros.
    inv LD.
    - eexists; split ; eauto.
      apply aval_lessdef_refl.
    -
      rewrite aadd_commut in ADD.
      simpl in ADD.
      destruct v1' ; try discriminate.
      inv ADD.
      eexists (Cval (Val.add v v')).
      split.
      simpl. destruct v; reflexivity.
      constructor. constructor.
  }
  inv LD1;
    inv LD2.
  - eexists ; split ; eauto. constructor.
  - eauto.
  - rewrite aadd_commut.
     rewrite aadd_commut in ADD.
     eauto.
  - inv H.
    + eauto.
    + simpl in ADD.
      inv ADD.
      eexists (Cval (Val.add v' v'0)).
      split ; repeat constructor.
      simpl.
      destruct v' ; reflexivity.
Qed.

  unfold eval_unary_cond in *.
  specialize (LD r).
  inv LD.
  - congruence.
  - rewrite <- H in *.
    inv H1. congruence.
    discriminate.

Lemma eval_binary_cond_lessdef :
  forall F rs rs' r1 r2 b
         (AT : eval_binary_cond F rs r1 r2 = Some b)
         (LD : aregset_lessdef rs rs'),
  eval_binary_cond F rs' r1 r2 = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eval_unary_cond in *.
  pose proof (LD r1) as P1.
  pose proof (LD r2) as P2.
  unfold eval_binary_cond in *.
  inv P1. inv P2.
  - congruence.
  - rewrite <- H in *.
    inv H2. congruence.
    destruct (rs r1) ; try discriminate.
    destruct v ; try discriminate.
  - rewrite <- H in *.
    inv H1.
    inv P2.
    congruence.
    rewrite <- H1 in *.
    inv H3. congruence.
    destruct v'; try discriminate.
    discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma aval_lessdef_cmpu :
  forall fptr fptr' cmp v1 v2 v1' v2'
         (PTR: forall (b0 : block) (ofs : Z), fptr b0 ofs = true -> fptr' b0 ofs = true),
    aval_lessdef v1 v1' ->
    (aval_lessdef v2 v2') ->
  aval_lessdef (alift2 (Val.cmpu fptr cmp) v1 v2)
    (alift2 (Val.cmpu fptr' cmp) v1' v2').
Proof.
    intros.
    unfold Val.cmpu.
    assert (CMPU : forall v1 v1' v2 v2',
               Val.lessdef v1 v1' ->
               Val.lessdef v2 v2' ->
               Val.lessdef (Val.of_optbool (Val.cmpu_bool fptr cmp v1 v2))
                           (Val.of_optbool (Val.cmpu_bool fptr' cmp v1' v2'))).
    {
      clear - PTR.
      intros.
      destruct (Val.cmpu_bool fptr cmp v1 v2) eqn:CMP.
      apply Val.cmpu_bool_lessdef
            with (valid_ptr':= fptr') (v1':= v1') (v2':= v2')
        in CMP;auto.
      rewrite CMP. constructor.
      constructor.
    }
    inv H. inv H0.
    - destruct v1',v2'; try constructor; auto.
    - destruct v1'; simpl; repeat constructor; auto.
    - inv H0.
      destruct v2' ; simpl.
      constructor; auto.
      constructor.
      constructor;auto.
  Qed.

Hint Resolve aval_lessdef_cmpu : ld.

Lemma acompare_int_lessdef : forall rs rs' v1 v1' v2 v2' m m',
    aregset_lessdef rs rs' ->
    aval_lessdef v1 v1' ->
    aval_lessdef v2 v2' ->
    Mem.extends m m' ->
    aregset_lessdef (acompare_int rs v1 v2 m) (acompare_int rs' v1' v2' m').
Proof.
  unfold acompare_int.
  intros.
  repeat apply aregset_set_lessdef; auto with ld.
  apply aval_lessdef_cmpu; auto.
  intros ; eapply Mem.valid_pointer_extends; eauto.
  apply aval_lessdef_cmpu; auto.
  intros ; eapply Mem.valid_pointer_extends; eauto.
Qed.

Hint Resolve acompare_int_lessdef : ld.

Definition lessdef_AmemSplit (x y: AmemSplit) :=
  match x , y with
  | SplitErr , SplitErr => True
  | SplitNIL , SplitNIL => True
  | SplitC l1 , SplitC l2 => list_forall2 memval_lessdef l1 l2
  | SplitA l1 , SplitA l2 => l1 = l2
  | _ , _ => False
  end.


Definition inject_AmemSplit (f:meminj) (x y: AmemSplit) :=
  match x , y with
  | SplitErr , SplitErr => True
  | SplitNIL , SplitNIL => True
  | SplitC l1 , SplitC l2 => list_forall2 (memval_inject f) l1 l2
  | SplitA l1 , SplitA l2 => l1 = l2
  | _ , _ => False
  end.

Lemma lessdef_AmemSplit_refl : forall x,
    lessdef_AmemSplit x x.
Proof.
  destruct x; simpl; auto.
  apply list_forall2_refl.
  intros. apply memval_lessdef_refl.
Qed.



Lemma split_amem_lessdef : forall l1 l2,
    list_forall2 amemval_lessdef l1 l2 ->
    lessdef_AmemSplit (split_amemval l1) (split_amemval l2).
Proof.
  intros.
  induction H.
  - simpl. auto.
  - simpl.
    inv H.
    destruct (split_amemval al), (split_amemval bl); try (simpl in *; auto; tauto);
      try apply lessdef_AmemSplit_refl.
    + simpl in IHlist_forall2.
      destruct b1; simpl.
      constructor ; auto. apply memval_lessdef_refl.
      auto.
    + simpl in IHlist_forall2.
      subst. apply lessdef_AmemSplit_refl.
    + destruct (split_amemval al), (split_amemval bl); try (simpl in *; auto; tauto);
      try apply lessdef_AmemSplit_refl.
          simpl. constructor ; auto. constructor.
          simpl. constructor ; auto.
Qed.

Inductive amemval_inject (f: meminj) : amemval -> amemval -> Prop :=
| Cmemval_inj : forall v v', memval_inject f v v' ->
                                 amemval_inject f (Cmemval v) (Cmemval v')
| Amemval_inj : forall s c n, amemval_inject f (Amemval s c n) (Amemval s c n).

Lemma split_amemval_inject : forall f l1 l2,
    list_forall2 (amemval_inject f) l1 l2 ->
    inject_AmemSplit f (split_amemval l1) (split_amemval l2).
Proof.
  intros.
  induction H.
  - simpl. auto.
  - simpl.
    inv H.
    destruct (split_amemval al), (split_amemval bl); try (simpl in *; auto; tauto).
    + simpl. constructor; auto.
      constructor.
    + simpl in IHlist_forall2.
      simpl.
      constructor ; auto.
    + destruct (split_amemval al), (split_amemval bl); simpl in *; try tauto.
      congruence.
Qed.

Lemma proj_bytes_Some :
  forall l1 l2 l,
         list_forall2 memval_lessdef l1 l2 ->
         proj_bytes l1 = Some l ->
         proj_bytes l2 = Some l.
Proof.
  intros l1 l2 l H.
  revert l.
  induction H.
  auto.
  inv H .
  - simpl.
    intros.
    destruct (proj_bytes al); try discriminate.
    inv H.
    erewrite IHlist_forall2; eauto.
  - simpl. congruence.
  - simpl. discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma astack_load_lessdef :
  forall chunk m m' stk stk' stkb ofs v,
    astack_load chunk m stk stkb ofs = Some v ->
    Mem.extends m m' ->
    astack_lessdef stk stk' ->
    exists v',
      astack_load chunk m' stk' stkb ofs = Some v' /\
        aval_lessdef v v'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold astack_load in *.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m chunk stkb ofs Readable); try discriminate.
  apply Mem.valid_access_extends with (m2:= m') in v0; auto.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m' chunk stkb ofs Readable); try tauto.
  assert (LD:
      option_rel aval_lessdef (decode_val chunk (getN (size_chunk_nat chunk) ofs stk)) (decode_val chunk (getN (size_chunk_nat chunk) ofs stk'))).
  {
    apply aval_lessdef_decode_val.
    apply list_forall2_getN; auto.
  }
  rewrite H in LD. inv LD.
  eexists ; split ; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_load_lessdef_gen :
  forall v v'
         (i : preg)
         (w : bool)
         chunk
    (rs : aregset)
    (stk : astack)
    (stkb : block)
    (m : mem)
    (rs' : aregset)
    (stk' : astack)
    (m0 : mem)
    (stkb' : block)
    (rs1 : aregset)
    (m1 : mem)
    (stk1 : astack)
    (H0 : aexec_load w chunk v i rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m0)
    (LD : aregset_lessdef rs rs1)
    (ME : Mem.extends m m1)
    (STK : astack_lessdef stk stk1)
    (LD1 : v <> None -> option_rel aval_lessdef v v')
  ,
  exists (rs2 : aregset) (stk2 : astack) (m2 : mem),
    aexec_load w chunk v' i rs1 stk1 stkb m1 = ANext rs2 stk2 stkb' m2 /\
    aregset_lessdef rs' rs2 /\ astack_lessdef stk' stk2 /\ Mem.extends m0 m2 /\ Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_bounds' m) m1 m2.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold aexec_load in *.
  destruct v ; try discriminate.
  specialize (LD1 ltac:(congruence)).
  inv LD1; try discriminate.
  destruct a ; try discriminate.
  +
    destruct v ; try discriminate.
      unfold Mem.loadv in H0.
       destruct (Mem.load chunk m b (Ptrofs.unsigned i0)) eqn:LOAD; try discriminate.
    inv H0.
    eapply Mem.load_extends in LOAD; eauto.
    destruct LOAD as (v2 & LOAD & LD2).
    assert (Hy : y = Cval (Vptr b i0)).
    {
      inv H1.
      reflexivity.
      inv H0.
      reflexivity.
    }
    rewrite Hy.
    unfold Mem.loadv.
    rewrite LOAD.
    do 3 eexists ; split_and ; try reflexivity; auto with ld.
    apply aregset_lessdef_anextinstr ;auto.
    apply aregset_set_lessdef. constructor ; auto.
    auto.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  +
    destruct (get_stack_offset v) eqn:GSO; try discriminate.
    destruct (astack_load chunk m stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i0)) eqn:ALOAD; try discriminate.
    inv H0.
    exploit astack_load_lessdef ; eauto.
    inv H1.
    intros (v1 & LOAD & LDV).
    rewrite GSO.
    rewrite LOAD.
    do 3 eexists.
    split_and; auto with ld.
    auto.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_load_lessdef :
  forall (i i0 : ireg)
         chunk
         (w : bool)
         (s : shift_op)
    (rs : aregset)
    (stk : astack)
    (stkb : block)
    (m : mem)
    (rs' : aregset)
    (stk' : astack)
    (m0 : mem)
    (stkb' : block)
    (rs1 : aregset)
    (m1 : mem)
    (stk1 : astack)
    (LD : aregset_lessdef rs rs1)
    (ME : Mem.extends m m1)
    (STK : astack_lessdef stk stk1)
    (H0 : aexec_load w chunk (aadd (rs i0) (aeval_shift_op s rs)) i rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m0),
  exists (rs2 : aregset) (stk2 : astack) (m2 : mem),
    aexec_load w chunk (aadd (rs1 i0) (aeval_shift_op s rs1)) i rs1 stk1 stkb m1 = ANext rs2 stk2 stkb' m2 /\
    aregset_lessdef rs' rs2 /\ astack_lessdef stk' stk2 /\ Mem.extends m0 m2 /\ Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_bounds' m) m1 m2.
Proof.
  intros.
  exploit aexec_load_lessdef_gen;eauto.
  intros.
  destruct ( (aadd (rs i0) (aeval_shift_op s rs))) eqn:AAD ; try congruence.
  apply aval_lessdef_aadd with (v1' := rs1 i0) (v2' := (aeval_shift_op s rs1)) in AAD ; auto with ld.
  destruct AAD as (r1 & AAD & LD1).
  rewrite AAD.
  constructor; auto.
Qed.

Lemma astack_store_extends :
  forall chunk m stk stkb o v stk' m1 stk1 v1,
    astack_store chunk m stk stkb o v = Some stk' ->
    Mem.extends m m1 ->
    astack_lessdef stk stk1 ->
    aval_lessdef v v1 ->
    exists stk2,
      astack_store chunk m1 stk1 stkb o v1 = Some stk2 /\
        astack_lessdef stk' stk2.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold astack_store in H.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m chunk stkb o Writable); try discriminate.
  exploit Mem.valid_access_extends; eauto.
  intro.
  unfold astack_store.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m1 chunk stkb o Writable); try tauto.
  apply encode_aval_lessdef with (chunk:= chunk) in H2; eauto.
  rename H2 into LD.
  inv LD. rewrite <- H4 in H. discriminate.
  rewrite <- H2 in H. inv H.
  eexists ; split; eauto.
  apply astack_lessdef_setN; auto.
Qed.

Lemma is_stack_pointer_inv : forall stkb' x y i,
    (is_stack_pointer stkb' x = Some i) ->
    (aval_lessdef x y) ->
    is_stack_pointer stkb' y = Some i.
Proof.
  unfold is_stack_pointer.
  intros. destruct x; try discriminate.
  destruct v ; try discriminate. inv H0. auto.
  inv H2. auto.
  inv H0. auto.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_store_extends : forall w chunk a v rs stk stkb m rs' stk' stkb' m' m1 rs1 stk1 a1,
    aexec_store w chunk a v rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m' ->
    Mem.extends m m1 ->
    aregset_lessdef rs rs1 ->
    astack_lessdef stk stk1 ->
    (a <> None -> option_rel aval_lessdef a a1) ->
    exists rs2 stk2 m2,
      aexec_store w chunk a1 v rs1 stk1 stkb m1 = ANext rs2 stk2 stkb' m2 /\
        aregset_lessdef rs' rs2 /\
        astack_lessdef stk' stk2 /\
        Mem.extends m' m2 /\
        Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_bounds' m) m1 m2.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold aexec_store,aexec_store' in H.
  destruct a ; try discriminate.
  destruct (is_stack_pointer stkb a) eqn:ISP; try discriminate.
  - specialize (H3 ltac:(congruence)).
    inv H3.
    destruct (astack_store chunk m stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i) (rs v)) eqn:AS; try discriminate.
    inv H.
    exploit astack_store_extends; eauto.
    intros (stk2 & STORE & LD).
    exploit is_stack_pointer_inv ; eauto.
    intros ISP1.
    unfold aexec_store. unfold aexec_store'.
    rewrite ISP1. rewrite STORE.
    do 3 eexists.
    split_and ; auto with ld.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  - destruct a ; try discriminate.
    + destruct (rs v) eqn:R ; try discriminate.
      unfold Mem.storev in H.
      destruct v0 ; try discriminate.
      destruct (Mem.store chunk m b (Ptrofs.unsigned i) v1) eqn:STORE ; try discriminate.
    inv H.
    unfold aexec_store,aexec_store'.
    specialize (H3 ltac:(congruence)).
    inv H3.
    assert (y = Cval (Vptr b i)).
    { inv H4. reflexivity. inv H3. reflexivity. }
    subst.
    pose proof (H1 v) as R1.
    rewrite R in R1.
    assert (exists v', rs1 v = Cval v' /\ Val.lessdef v1 v').
    {
      inv R1.
      eexists. split; eauto.
      eexists. split; eauto.
    }
    destruct H as (v' & EQ & LD).
    rewrite EQ.
    unfold Mem.storev.
    exploit Mem.store_within_extends; eauto.
    intros (m2' & STOR2 & EXT2).
    rewrite STOR2.
    do 3 eexists; split_and; eauto with ld.
    rewrite ISP. reflexivity.
    eapply Mem.store_unchanged_on; eauto.
    unfold loc_out_of_bounds'; intros.
    intro.
    destruct H3.
    assert (Mem.perm m b i0 Max Nonempty).
    { apply Mem.perm_cur_max. apply Mem.perm_implies with Writable; auto with mem.
    exploit Mem.store_valid_access_3. eexact STORE. intros [P Q]. eauto. }
    unfold loc_out_of_bounds in H5.
    tauto.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_instr_extends :
  forall w i rs stk stkb m rs' stk' m0 stkb' rs1 m1 stk1
    (EX: aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m0)
    (LD : aregset_lessdef rs rs1)
    (ME : Mem.extends m m1)
    (STK : astack_lessdef stk stk1),
  exists (rs2 : aregset) (stk2 : astack) (m2:mem),
    aexec_instr w i rs1 stk1 stkb m1 =
      ANext rs2 stk2 stkb' m2 /\
      aregset_lessdef rs' rs2 /\
      astack_lessdef stk' stk2 /\
      Mem.extends m0 m2 /\
      Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_bounds' m) m1 m2.
Proof.
  intros.
  generalize Mem.extends_refl.
  generalize Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  intros.
  Ltac case_binop :=
    simpl;
    do 3 eexists;
    split_and; try reflexivity ; auto 20 with ld;fail.

  destruct i eqn:I ; simpl in EX; inv EX ;
    try (simpl;
    exploit aexec_load_lessdef; eauto;auto with ld;fail);
    try (simpl ; exploit aexec_store_extends; eauto; fail);
    try (case_binop).
  - simpl.
      destruct (aadd (rs i1) (aeval_shift_op s rs)) eqn: ADD ; try discriminate.
      inv H2.
      * apply aval_lessdef_aadd with (v1' := rs1 i1) (v2' := (aeval_shift_op s rs1))in ADD; eauto with ld.
        destruct ADD as (r' & AADD1 & LD1 ).
        rewrite AADD1.
        do 3 eexists.
        split_and.
        reflexivity.
        all: auto with ld.
  - simpl.
    destruct (aeval_testcond t rs) eqn:AE; try discriminate.
    apply aeval_testcond_lessdef with (2:= LD) in AE.
    rewrite AE.
    destruct b.
    + unfold agoto_label in *.
      inv H2.
      do 3 eexists; split_and; eauto with ld.
    + inv H2.
      do 3 eexists; split_and; eauto with ld.
  - simpl.
    destruct (aadd (alift2 Val.mul (rs i1) (rs i2)) (rs i3)) eqn:AADD;
      try discriminate.
    inv H2.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in AADD; eauto.
    destruct AADD as (r' & ADD & LD1).
    rewrite ADD.
    do 3 eexists ; split_and; eauto with ld.
    auto with ld.
  - simpl.
    exploit aexec_store_extends; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i1) (aeval_shift_op s rs)) eqn:A; try discriminate.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in A ; eauto.
    destruct A as (r' & EQ & LD1).
    rewrite EQ. constructor. auto.
    auto with ld.
  - simpl.
    exploit aexec_store_extends; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i1) (aeval_shift_op s rs)) eqn:A; try discriminate.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in A ; eauto.
    destruct A as (r' & EQ & LD1).
    rewrite EQ. constructor. auto.
    auto with ld.
  - simpl.
    exploit aexec_store_extends; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i1) (aeval_shift_op s rs)) eqn:A; try discriminate.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in A ; eauto.
    destruct A as (r' & EQ & LD1).
    rewrite EQ. constructor. auto.
    auto with ld.
  - simpl.
    exploit aexec_store_extends; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i1) (aeval_shift_op s rs)) eqn:A; try discriminate.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in A ; eauto.
    destruct A as (r' & EQ & LD1).
    rewrite EQ. constructor. auto.
    auto with ld.
  - simpl.
    destruct (adivs (rs IR0) (rs IR1)) eqn:DIV; try discriminate.
    inv H2.
    exploit aval_lessdef_adivs; eauto.
    intros(a' & D& LD1).
    rewrite D. do 3 eexists ; split_and ; eauto 20 with ld.
  - simpl.
    destruct (adivu (rs IR0) (rs IR1)) eqn:DIV; try discriminate.
    inv H2.
    exploit aval_lessdef_adivu; eauto.
    intros(a' & D& LD1).
    rewrite D. do 3 eexists ; split_and ; eauto 20 with ld.
  - simpl.
    exploit aexec_load_lessdef_gen; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i0) (Cval (Vint i1))) eqn:AADD; try congruence.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in AADD; eauto.
    destruct AADD as (r1 & EQ1 & LD1).
    rewrite EQ1. constructor ; auto.
    constructor.
  - simpl.
    exploit aexec_load_lessdef_gen; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i0) (Cval (Vint i1))) eqn:AADD; try congruence.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in AADD; eauto.
    destruct AADD as (r1 & EQ1 & LD1).
    rewrite EQ1. constructor ; auto.
    constructor.
  - simpl.
    simpl.
    exploit aexec_load_lessdef_gen; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i0) (Cval (Vint i1))) eqn:AADD; try congruence.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in AADD; eauto.
    destruct AADD as (r1 & EQ1 & LD1).
    rewrite EQ1. constructor ; auto.
    constructor.
  - simpl.
    exploit aexec_store_extends; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i0) (Cval (Vint i1))) eqn:A; try discriminate.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in A ; eauto.
    destruct A as (r' & EQ & LD1).
    rewrite EQ. constructor. auto.
    auto with ld.
  - simpl.
    exploit aexec_store_extends; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i0) (Cval (Vint i1))) eqn:A; try discriminate.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in A ; eauto.
    destruct A as (r' & EQ & LD1).
    rewrite EQ. constructor. auto.
    auto with ld.
  - simpl.
    exploit aexec_store_extends; eauto.
    intros.
    destruct (aadd (rs i0) (Cval (Vint i1))) eqn:A; try discriminate.
    eapply aval_lessdef_aadd in A ; eauto.
    destruct A as (r' & EQ & LD1).
    rewrite EQ. constructor. auto.
    auto with ld.
Qed.
