Lemma bin_interp_extends :
  forall rt n rs rs1 stk stk1 stkb m m1 vres m2
         (I : bin_interp rt n rs stk stkb m =
                Some (vres, m2))
         (LD : aregset_lessdef rs rs1)
         (ME : Mem.extends m m1)
         (STK : astack_lessdef stk stk1),
  exists vres' m2',
    bin_interp rt n rs1 stk1 stkb m1 = Some (vres',m2') /\
      Val.lessdef vres vres' /\
      Mem.extends m2 m2' /\
      Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_bounds' m) m1 m2'.
Proof.
  induction n.
  - simpl.
    intros. destruct (is_final_state rs) eqn:RS; try discriminate.
    rewrite is_final_state_lessdef with (rs:=rs) ; auto.
    rewrite RS.
    exploit get_result_inv_mem; eauto.
    intro.
    apply get_result_lessdef with (v':= rs1 IR0) (m1:=m1) in I.
    destruct I as (vres' & GR & LDR).
    rewrite GR. eexists. eexists. split_and; auto.
    congruence.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
    apply LD.
  - intros.
    simpl in I.
    simpl.
    rewrite is_final_state_lessdef with (rs:=rs);auto.
    destruct (is_final_state rs) eqn:F ; try discriminate.
    + simpl.
      exploit get_result_lessdef ; eauto.
      intros (vres' & GR & LDR).
      rewrite GR.
      do 2 eexists; split_and; auto.
      apply get_result_inv_mem in I.
      subst. auto.
      apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
    + simpl.
      destruct (find_instr (rs PC)) as [(i,w)|]eqn:FI ; try discriminate.
      exploit find_instr_lessded ; eauto.
      intro H ; rewrite H.
      destruct (aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m) eqn:AI; try discriminate.
      rename a into rs'.
      rename a0 into stk'.
      rename b into stkb'.
      exploit aexec_instr_extends ; eauto.
      intros (rs2 & stk2 & m3 & EI & ALD & ASKLD & EXT & UNC).
      rewrite EI.
      exploit IHn ; eauto.
      intros (vres' & m2' & BINTP & LD' & EXT' & UNC').
      do 2 eexists ; split_and; eauto.
      eapply Mem.unchanged_on_trans;eauto.
      eapply Mem.unchanged_on_implies;eauto.
      unfold loc_out_of_bounds',loc_out_of_bounds.
      intros.
      assert (Mem.valid_block m0 b).
      {
        rewrite Mem.valid_block_extends by eauto.
        auto.
      }
      destruct H0. split ; auto.
      intro.
      eapply aexec_instr_perm in AI; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma bin_exec_sem_extends :
  forall n s sz pos ge vargs vargs' m1 m1' t vres m2
         (EXEC : bin_exec_sem n s sz pos ge vargs m1 t vres m2)

  econstructor ; eauto.
  unfold bin_exec. rewrite I'.
  eauto.
  auto.
  auto.
  eapply Mem.unchanged_on_trans;eauto.
  eapply Mem.unchanged_on_implies.
  eauto.
  repeat intro.
  unfold loc_out_of_bounds' in H. unfold loc_out_of_bounds'.
  destruct H.
  split.
  eapply init_state_valid_block in I; eauto.
  unfold loc_out_of_bounds in *.
  intro.
  apply H1.
  eapply init_state_perm in I ; eauto.
Qed.

Inductive aval_inject (f : meminj) : aval -> aval -> Prop :=
| aval_inj_cval : forall c c', Val.inject f c c' -> aval_inject f (Cval c) (Cval c')
| aval_inj_aval : forall s, aval_inject f (Aval s) (Aval s).


Definition astack_inject (f:meminj) (s s': astack) :=
  forall i, amemval_inject f (ZMap.get i s) (ZMap.get i s').


Definition aregset_inject (f: meminj) (rs rs' : aregset) : Prop :=
  forall r, aval_inject f (rs r) (rs' r).

Lemma alloc_arguments_inject:
  forall (f:meminj) (vargs vargs' : list val) (args : list typ)
    (regs : list mreg) (l : list (preg * val))
    (VI : Val.inject_list f vargs vargs')
    (AA : alloc_arguments vargs args regs = Some l),
  exists l' : list (preg * val),
    alloc_arguments vargs' args regs = Some l' /\
    list_forall2
      (fun rv rv' : preg * val =>
       fst rv = fst rv' /\ Val.inject f (snd rv) (snd rv')) l l'.
Proof.
  intros.
  revert args regs l AA.
  induction VI.
  - simpl.
    destruct args; try discriminate.
    simpl ; intros.
    inv AA.
    exists nil.
    split ; auto.
    constructor.
  - simpl.
    destruct args ; try discriminate.
    destruct t ; try discriminate.
    destruct regs ; try discriminate.
    intros.
    destruct (alloc_arguments vl args regs) eqn:AA'; try discriminate.
    inv AA.
    apply IHVI in AA'.
    destruct AA' as (l' & AA2 & FA).
    rewrite AA2.
    exists ((preg_of m,v')::l').
    split ; auto.
    constructor; auto.
Qed.

Lemma astack_inject_set : forall f n v1 stk1 v2 stk2,
    astack_inject f stk1 stk2 ->
    amemval_inject f v1 v2 ->
    astack_inject f (ZMap.set n v1 stk1) (ZMap.set n v2 stk2).
Proof.
  repeat intro.
  rewrite !ZMap.gsspec.
  destruct (ZIndexed.eq i n). auto.
  apply H.
Qed.


Lemma astack_inject_setN:
  forall f (l1 l2 : list amemval) (n : Z) (stk1 stk2 : astack),
  astack_inject f stk1 stk2 ->
  list_forall2 (amemval_inject f) l1 l2 ->
  astack_inject f (setN l1 n stk1) (setN l2 n stk2).
Proof.
  intros.
  revert stk1 stk2 n H.
  induction H0.
  - simpl. auto.
  - simpl.
    intros.
    apply IHlist_forall2.
    apply astack_inject_set; auto.
Qed.

Lemma forall2_amemval_inject_Undef : forall f n,
  list_forall2 (amemval_inject f)
    (map Cmemval (repeat Undef n))
    (map Cmemval (repeat Undef n)).
Proof.
  intros.
  apply list_forall2_refl'.
  intros.
  rewrite in_map_iff in H. destruct H as (mv & EQ & IN).
  subst. constructor.
  apply repeat_spec in IN. subst. constructor.
Qed.


Lemma encode_aval_inject:
  forall f (chunk : memory_chunk) (v1 v2 : aval),
  aval_inject f v1 v2 ->
  option_rel (list_forall2 (amemval_inject f)) (encode_aval chunk v1) (encode_aval chunk v2).
Proof.
  intros. inv H.
  - unfold encode_aval.
    constructor.
    apply list_forall2_map.
    exploit encode_val_inject;eauto.
    apply list_forall2_implies.
    intros ; constructor;auto.
  - unfold encode_aval.
    unfold encode_sval.
    destruct (typ_of_sval s) eqn:TC;
      try apply forall2_amemval_inject_Undef; try constructor.
    destruct (rchunk_of_chunk chunk) eqn:RC.
    repeat constructor.
    constructor.
Qed.




Lemma astack_store_inject :
  forall f chunk m1 m2 stk1 stkb stkb' v1 v2 x stk1' stk2
         (FSTACK : f stkb = Some(stkb',0))
         (MEXT : Mem.inject f m1 m2)
         (STORE: astack_store chunk m1 stk1 stkb x v1 = Some stk1')
         (ASTKLD : astack_inject f stk1 stk2)
         (AVALLD : aval_inject f v1 v2),
         exists stk2',
           astack_store chunk m2 stk2 stkb' x v2 = Some stk2'
           /\
             astack_inject f stk1' stk2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold astack_store in *.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m1 chunk stkb x Writable);
    try discriminate.
  exploit Mem.valid_access_inject; eauto.
  intro ACC.
  replace (x + 0) with x in ACC by lia.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m2 chunk stkb' x Writable); try tauto.
  apply encode_aval_inject with (chunk:= chunk) in AVALLD.
  inv AVALLD.
  rewrite <- H0 in STORE; discriminate.
  rewrite <- H in STORE. inv STORE.
  eexists.
  split. reflexivity.
  apply astack_inject_setN; auto.
Qed.


Lemma aregset_inject_set : forall f rs rs' x v v',
    aval_inject f v v' ->
    aregset_inject f rs rs' ->
    aregset_inject f (rs # x <- v) (rs' # x <- v').
Proof.
  intros.
  intro.
  destruct (preg_eq x r).
  - subst.
    rewrite! Pregmap.gss.
    auto.
  - rewrite! Pregmap.gso by congruence.
    auto.
Qed.

Hint Resolve aregset_inject_set : inject.

Record augment_meminj (f:meminj) (f':meminj) (b b':block) :=
  {
    augment_not_alloc : forall x, x <> b -> f x = f' x;
    augment_free : f b = None;
    augment_alloc : f' b = Some(b',0)
  }.

Definition loc_unmapped' (f:meminj) (m : mem) (b:block) (z:Z) :=
  Mem.valid_block m b /\ loc_unmapped f b z.

Definition loc_out_of_reach' (f:meminj) (m : mem) (m1:mem) (b:block) (z:Z) :=
  Mem.valid_block m1 b /\ loc_out_of_reach f m b z.

Lemma allocframe_inject :
  forall (f:meminj) sz pos m1 m2 rs rs' stk stkb m1' rs2
         (I : allocframe sz pos m1 rs = ANext rs2 stk stkb m2)
         (ALD : aregset_inject f rs rs')
         (EXTEND : Mem.inject f m1 m1'),
  exists (f': meminj) (rs2' : aregset) (stk': astack) (stkb':block) (m2' : mem),
    allocframe sz pos m1' rs' = ANext rs2' stk' stkb' m2' /\
      augment_meminj f f' stkb stkb' /\
      Mem.inject f' m2 m2' /\
      aregset_inject f' rs2 rs2' /\
      astack_inject f' stk stk' /\
      Mem.unchanged_on (loc_unmapped' f m1) m1 m2 /\
      Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_reach' f m1 m1') m1' m2' /\
      inject_incr f f' /\ inject_separated f f' m1 m1'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold allocframe in I.
  destruct (Mem.alloc m1 0 sz) eqn:A.
  simpl in I.
  destruct_in I eq:STORE; try discriminate.
  inv I.
  unfold allocframe.
  assert (A1 := A).
  eapply Mem.alloc_parallel_inject with (f:=f) (m2:=m1') (lo2 := 0) (hi2 := sz) in A; auto; try lia.
  destruct A as (f' & m3' & b2 & A' & INJ' & INC & SPEC1 & SPEC2).
  rename b2 into stkb'.
  rewrite A'.
  simpl.
  apply astack_store_inject with (f:=f') (m2:= m3') (v2:= (rs' IR13)) (stkb':= stkb')
                                  (stk2 := (ZMap.init (Cmemval Undef)))
    in STORE; eauto.
  destruct STORE as (stk2' & STORE & INJ).
  rewrite STORE.
  do 5 eexists. split_and; eauto with inject.
  - constructor; auto.
    + intro. symmetry; auto.
    +
      specialize (INC stkb).
      destruct (f stkb) eqn:FSTK; auto.
      destruct p.
      eapply Mem.valid_block_inject_1 in FSTK; eauto.
      eapply Mem.fresh_block_alloc in A1.
      tauto.
  - eapply Mem.alloc_unchanged_on;eauto.
  - eapply Mem.alloc_unchanged_on; eauto.
  - unfold inject_separated. intros.
    destruct (eq_block b1 stkb).
    subst. rewrite SPEC1 in H0.
    inv H0.
    split.
    eapply Mem.fresh_block_alloc; eauto.
    eapply Mem.fresh_block_alloc; eauto.
    rewrite SPEC2 in H0 by assumption. congruence.
  - apply astack_inject_init.
  - eauto with inject.
Qed.

Lemma update_regset_inject :
  forall f l l'
         (A_LD : list_forall2
             (fun rv rv' : preg * aval =>
                fst rv = fst rv' /\ aval_inject f (snd rv) (snd rv')) l
             l')
         rs rs'
         (RS_LD : aregset_inject f rs rs')
,
         aregset_inject f (update_regset l rs) (update_regset l' rs').
Proof.
  intros f l l' A_LD.
  induction A_LD.
  - simpl. auto.
  - simpl.
    intros.
    destruct a1, b1.
    simpl in *. destruct H ; subst.
    intro.
    apply aregset_inject_set. auto.
    apply IHA_LD; auto.
Qed.


Lemma init_regset_inject :
  forall f l l'
         (A_LD : list_forall2
             (fun rv rv' : preg * val =>
                fst rv = fst rv' /\ Val.inject f (snd rv) (snd rv')) l
             l')
         rs rs'
         (RS_LD : aregset_inject f rs rs')
,
         aregset_inject f (init_regset l rs) (init_regset l' rs').
Proof.
  intros f l l' A_LD.
  intros.
  unfold init_regset.
  apply update_regset_inject; auto.
  apply list_forall2_map.
  eapply list_forall2_implies; eauto.
  simpl. destruct x,y; simpl.
  intuition subst. constructor ; auto.
Qed.

Lemma init_state_inject :
  forall s sz pos f m1 m1' vargs vargs' rs stk stkb m2
         (INJ : Mem.inject f m1 m1')
         (VINJ : Val.inject_list f vargs vargs')
         (INIT : init_state s sz pos vargs m1 = ANext rs stk stkb m2),
  exists (f': meminj) (rs' : aregset) (stk': astack) (stkb':block) (m2' : mem),
    init_state s sz pos vargs' m1' = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m2' /\
      augment_meminj f f' stkb stkb' /\
      aregset_inject f' rs rs' /\
      astack_inject f' stk stk' /\
      Mem.inject f' m2 m2' /\
      Mem.unchanged_on (loc_unmapped' f m1) m1 m2 /\
      Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_reach' f m1 m1') m1' m2' /\
      inject_incr f f' /\ inject_separated f f' m1 m1'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold init_state in INIT.
  destruct (alloc_arguments vargs (sig_args s) int_param_regs) eqn:ALLOC; try discriminate.
  unfold init_state.
  destruct_in INIT eq:AF; try discriminate.
  exploit alloc_arguments_inject; eauto.
  intros (l' & ALLOC'& INJ').
  rewrite ALLOC'. inv INIT.
  assert (INJRS0 : aregset_inject f (init_regset l regset0) (init_regset l' regset0)).
  {
    apply init_regset_inject; eauto.
    apply aregset_inject_regset0.
  }
  exploit allocframe_inject ; eauto.
  intros (f' & rs2' & stk' & stkb' & m2' & ALLOC1 & INJ1 & AREG & ASTCK &
            UNCH1 & UNCH2 & INCR & SEP & FB).
  rewrite ALLOC1.
  do 5 eexists; split_and; eauto.
  apply aregset_inject_set.
  apply init_regset_inject.
  revert SEP.
  revert INJ'.
  clear - trace E0. intro.
  induction INJ'.
  constructor.
  intros.
  constructor ; auto.
  destruct H.
  split; auto.
  eapply val_inject_incr ; eauto.
  apply aregset_inject_regset0; auto.
  apply aregset_inject_set;auto.
  constructor.
Qed.

Lemma aval_inject_aadd :
  forall f v1 v2 v1' v2' r
         (ADD : aadd v1 v2 = Some r)
         (LD1 : aval_inject f v1 v1')
         (LD2 : aval_inject f v2 v2')
  ,
    exists r', (aadd v1' v2') = Some r' /\ aval_inject f r r'.
Proof.
  intros.
  inv LD1.
  inv LD2.
  - rewrite aadd_cval in ADD.
  inv ADD.
  rewrite aadd_cval.
  eexists ; split_and; eauto.
  constructor; auto with inject.
  - simpl in ADD.
  destruct c; try congruence.
  destruct s; try discriminate.
  inv ADD.
  inv H. eexists; split_and.
  simpl. reflexivity.
  constructor.
  - inv LD2.
    + rewrite aadd_commut in ADD.
      simpl in ADD.
      destruct c; try congruence.
      destruct s; try discriminate. inv ADD.
      inv H. eexists; split_and.
      simpl. reflexivity.
      constructor.
    + simpl in ADD.
       destruct s ; discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma eval_unary_cond_inject f :
  forall F rs rs' r b
         (AT : eval_unary_cond F rs r = Some b)
         (LD : aregset_inject f rs rs'),
  eval_unary_cond F rs' r = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eval_unary_cond in *.
  specialize (LD r).
  inv LD.
  - rewrite <- H in AT. destruct c ; try congruence.
    inv AT. inv H1. reflexivity.
  - rewrite <- H0 in *.
    discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma eval_binary_cond_inject f :
  forall F rs rs' r1 r2 b
         (AT : eval_binary_cond F rs r1 r2 = Some b)
         (LD : aregset_inject f rs rs'),
  eval_binary_cond F rs' r1 r2 = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eval_unary_cond in *.
  pose proof (LD r1) as P1.
  pose proof (LD r2) as P2.
  unfold eval_binary_cond in *.
  inv P1. inv P2.
  - rewrite <- H in *.
    destruct c ; try congruence.
    rewrite <- H2 in AT. destruct c0 ; try congruence.
    inv H1. inv H4. auto.
  - rewrite <- H in *.
    destruct c ; try discriminate.
    rewrite <- H3 in *. discriminate.
  - rewrite <- H0 in *. discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma eval_ternary_cond_inject f :
  forall F rs rs' r1 r2 r3 b
         (AT : eval_ternary_cond F rs r1 r2 r3 = Some b)
         (LD : aregset_inject f rs rs'),
  eval_ternary_cond F rs' r1 r2 r3 = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eval_ternary_cond in *.
  pose proof (LD r1) as P1.
  inv P1.
  destruct (rs r1); try discriminate.
  destruct v; try discriminate.
  inv H. inv H1.
  eapply eval_binary_cond_inject;eauto.
  rewrite <- H0 in AT. discriminate.
Qed.



Lemma aeval_testcond_inject f :
  forall t rs rs' b
         (AT : aeval_testcond t rs = Some b)
         (LD : aregset_inject f rs rs'),
    aeval_testcond t rs' = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  pose proof (LD CZ) as LDCZ.
  pose proof (LD CC) as LDCC.
  pose proof (LD CN) as LDCN.
  destruct t ; simpl in *;
    try (eapply eval_unary_cond_inject ; eauto; fail);
  try (eapply eval_binary_cond_inject ; eauto; fail).
  - eapply eval_ternary_cond_inject ; eauto; fail.
  - eapply eval_ternary_cond_inject ; eauto; fail.
Qed.

Lemma val_sub_inject f : forall v1 v1' v2 v2',
    Val.inject f v1 v1' ->
    Val.inject f v2 v2' ->
    Val.inject f (Val.sub v1 v2) (Val.sub v1' v2').
Proof.
  intros.
  inv H; try constructor.
  - inv H0; try constructor.
  - inv H0; try constructor.
    simpl. destruct Archi.ptr64; try constructor.
    econstructor; eauto.
    rewrite Ptrofs.sub_add_l.
    reflexivity.
    simpl. destruct Archi.ptr64; try constructor.
    destruct (eq_block b1 b0); subst.
    destruct (eq_block b2 b3); subst.
    rewrite H1 in H. inv H.
    assert ((Ptrofs.sub ofs1 ofs0) =
              (Ptrofs.sub (Ptrofs.add ofs1 (Ptrofs.repr delta0))
                          (Ptrofs.add ofs0 (Ptrofs.repr delta0)))).
    {
      rewrite !Ptrofs.sub_add_opp.
      rewrite Ptrofs.add_assoc.
      f_equal.
      rewrite (Ptrofs.add_commut ofs0).
      rewrite Ptrofs.neg_add_distr.
      rewrite <- Ptrofs.add_assoc.
      rewrite Ptrofs.add_neg_zero.
      rewrite Ptrofs.add_zero_l.
      reflexivity.
    }
    rewrite <- H.
    constructor.
    congruence.
    constructor.
Qed.

Hint Resolve val_sub_inject : inject.

Lemma cmpu_inject : forall f m tm c v1 tv1 v2 tv2
    (H0 : Val.inject f v1 tv1)
    (H1 : Val.inject f v2 tv2)
    (H2 : Mem.inject f m tm),
    Val.inject f (Val.cmpu (Mem.valid_pointer m) c v1 v2) (Val.cmpu (Mem.valid_pointer tm) c tv1 tv2).
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold Val.cmpu.
  destruct (Val.cmpu_bool (Mem.valid_pointer m) c v1 v2) as [b|] eqn:E.
  replace (Val.cmpu_bool (Mem.valid_pointer tm) c tv1 tv2) with (Some b).
  apply val_inject_val_of_optbool.
  symmetry. eapply Val.cmpu_bool_inject; eauto.
  intros; eapply Mem.valid_pointer_inject_val; eauto.
  intros; eapply Mem.weak_valid_pointer_inject_val; eauto.
  intros; eapply Mem.weak_valid_pointer_inject_no_overflow; eauto.
  intros; eapply Mem.different_pointers_inject; eauto.
  simpl; auto.
Qed.

Lemma acompare_int_inject f : forall rs rs' v1 v1' v2 v2' m m',
    aregset_inject f rs rs' ->
    aval_inject f v1 v1' ->
    aval_inject f v2 v2' ->
    Mem.inject f m m' ->
    aregset_inject f (acompare_int rs v1 v2 m) (acompare_int rs' v1' v2' m').
Proof.
  unfold acompare_int.
  intros.
  repeat apply aregset_inject_set; auto with inject.
  - inv H0; inv H1 ; repeat constructor.
    eapply cmpu_inject; eauto.
  - inv H0; inv H1 ; repeat constructor.
    eapply cmpu_inject; eauto.
  - inv H0; inv H1 ; repeat constructor.
    apply val_negative_inject.
    eauto with inject.
Qed.

Lemma aval_inject_proj_value_refl : forall chunk f l,
    option_rel (aval_inject f) (proj_value chunk l) (proj_value chunk l).
Proof.
  unfold proj_value.
  intros.
  destruct (rchunk_of_chunk chunk) eqn:RC.
  -
  destruct l.
  + constructor.
  + destruct p. destruct p.
    destruct (rchunk_eq r r0 && check_value 4 s r0 ((s, r0, n) :: l)).
    constructor. constructor. constructor.
  - repeat constructor.
Qed.

Lemma astack_load_inject :
  forall chunk f m m1 stk stk1 stkb stkb1 ofs v
         (INJ : Mem.inject f m m1)
         (SINJ : astack_inject f stk stk1)
         (FB : f stkb = Some (stkb1, 0))
         (LOAD : astack_load chunk m stk stkb ofs = Some v),
  exists v1,
    astack_load chunk m1 stk1 stkb1 ofs = Some v1 /\
      aval_inject f v v1.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold astack_load in *.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m chunk stkb ofs Readable) ;
    try discriminate.
  inv LOAD.
  exploit Mem.valid_access_inject; eauto.
  intro.
  replace (ofs + 0) with ofs in H by lia.
  destruct (Mem.valid_access_dec m1 chunk stkb1 ofs Readable);
    try tauto.
  unfold astack_inject in SINJ.
  apply list_forall2_amemval_inject_getN with (n:= size_chunk_nat chunk) (ofs:=ofs) in SINJ.
  unfold decode_val in *.
  revert SINJ H0.
  generalize (getN (size_chunk_nat chunk) ofs stk) as l1.
  generalize (getN (size_chunk_nat chunk) ofs stk1) as l2.
  intros.
  apply split_amemval_inject in SINJ.
  destruct (split_amemval l1),(split_amemval l2); simpl in *;
    try congruence; try tauto.
  - inv H0. eexists. split_and. reflexivity.
    constructor. apply decode_val_inject; auto.
  - subst. eexists. split_and. eauto.
    assert (option_rel (aval_inject f) (Some v) (Some v)).
    { rewrite <- H0.
      eapply aval_inject_proj_value_refl. }
    inv H1. auto.
Qed.


Lemma aexec_load_inject :
  forall w chunk f v rs stk stkb rs' stk' stkb' m' i m m1 rs1 stk1 v1 stkb1
    (BEXEC : aexec_load w chunk v i rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m')
    (INJ : Mem.inject f m m1)
    (RINJ : aregset_inject f rs rs1)
    (SINJ : astack_inject f stk stk1)
    (FB : f stkb = Some (stkb1, 0))
    (INJV : v <> None -> option_rel (aval_inject f) v v1),
  exists

    aexec_load w chunk v1 i rs1 stk1 stkb1 m1 = ANext rs2' stk2' stkb2' m2' /\

    astack_inject f stk' stk2' /\

    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_unmapped' f m) m m' /\
    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_reach' f m m1) m1 m2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct v; try discriminate.
  specialize (INJV ltac:(congruence)).
  inv INJV.
  simpl in BEXEC.
  inv H0.
  - destruct (Mem.loadv chunk m c) eqn:LOAD ; try discriminate.
    inv BEXEC.
    exploit Mem.loadv_inject; eauto.
    intros (v2' & LOADV & INJ2).
    do 4 eexists.
    simpl. rewrite LOADV.
    split_and ; try reflexivity; eauto with inject.
    (*** *)
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  -
    destruct (get_stack_offset s) eqn:GSO ; try discriminate.
    destruct (astack_load chunk m stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i0))
             eqn: LOAD;try discriminate.
    inv BEXEC.
    unfold aexec_load.
    rewrite GSO.
    exploit astack_load_inject; eauto.
    intros (a1 & LOAD1 & INJ1).
    simpl. rewrite LOAD1.
    do 4 eexists.
    split_and; auto.
    apply aregset_anextinstr_inject.
    apply aregset_inject_set; auto.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
Qed.

Lemma aval_inject_aadd_rel : forall f a1 a1' a2 a2',
    aval_inject f a1 a1' ->
    aval_inject f a2 a2' ->

    option_rel (aval_inject f) (aadd a1 a2) (aadd a1' a2').

  intros.

  eapply aval_inject_aadd in AADD; eauto.

  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma is_stack_pointer_inj : forall f stkb stkb' x y i,
    (is_stack_pointer stkb x = Some i) ->
    (aval_inject f x y) ->
    f stkb = Some(stkb',0) ->
    is_stack_pointer stkb' y = Some i.
Proof.
  unfold is_stack_pointer.
  intros. destruct x; try discriminate.
  destruct v ; try discriminate. inv H0. inv H3.
  destruct (eq_block b stkb); try discriminate. subst.
  - destruct (eq_block b2 stkb'); try congruence.
    assert (delta = 0) by congruence.
    subst. rewrite Ptrofs.add_zero. auto.
  - inv H0. auto.
Qed.


Record inj_stack (stkb stkb':block) (f: meminj) :=
  {
    f_stkb : f stkb = Some(stkb',0);
    f_not_stkb : forall b d, f b = Some (stkb',d) -> b = stkb
  }.



Lemma aexec_store_inject :
  forall w chunk f v rs stk stkb rs' stk' stkb' m' i m m1 rs1 stk1 v1 stkb1
    (BEXEC : aexec_store w chunk v i rs stk stkb m = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m')
    (INJ : Mem.inject f m m1)
    (RINJ : aregset_inject f rs rs1)
    (SINJ : astack_inject f stk stk1)
    (ISTK : inj_stack stkb stkb1 f)
    (INJV : v <> None -> option_rel (aval_inject f) v v1),
  exists
    (rs2' : aregset) (stk2' : astack)
  (stkb2' : block) (m2' : mem),
    aexec_store w chunk v1 i rs1 stk1 stkb1 m1 = ANext rs2' stk2' stkb2' m2' /\
    aregset_inject f rs' rs2' /\
    astack_inject f stk' stk2' /\
    Mem.inject f m' m2' /\
    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_unmapped' f m) m m' /\
    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_reach' f m m1) m1 m2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold aexec_store in *.
  destruct v; try discriminate.
  specialize (INJV ltac:(congruence)).
  inv INJV.
  simpl in BEXEC.
  destruct (is_stack_pointer stkb a) eqn:ISP;try discriminate.
  -
    destruct ISTK.
    exploit is_stack_pointer_inj;eauto.
    destruct (astack_store chunk m stk stkb
                           (Ptrofs.unsigned i0) (rs i)) eqn:
      STORE ; try discriminate.
    inv BEXEC.
    exploit astack_store_inject; eauto.
    intros (stk2 & STORE2 & INJ').
    do 4 eexists; split_and;try reflexivity ; auto with inject.
    simpl. rewrite H.
    rewrite STORE2. reflexivity.
    auto with inject.
    auto with inject. auto with inject.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
    apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  -
    destruct a; try discriminate.
    inv H0.
    destruct (rs i) eqn: RS ; try discriminate.
    cbn - [is_stack_pointer].
    generalize (RINJ i).
    rewrite RS. intro RINi.
    inv RINi.
    destruct (Mem.storev chunk m v v0) eqn:STORE; try discriminate.
    inv BEXEC.
    exploit Mem.storev_mapped_inject; eauto.
    intros (m2 & STORE2 & INJ2).
    unfold Mem.storev in *.
    destruct v ; try discriminate.
    inv H1.
    simpl in ISP. destruct (eq_block b stkb'); try discriminate.
    assert (SPN: is_stack_pointer stkb1
          (Cval (Vptr b2 (Ptrofs.add i0 (Ptrofs.repr delta)))) = None).
    {
      simpl. destruct (eq_block b2 stkb1); try reflexivity.
      subst.
      exfalso.
      apply n. eapply f_not_stkb; eauto.
    }
    rewrite SPN.
    rewrite STORE2.
    do 4 eexists.
    split_and ; try reflexivity; eauto with inject.
    +
      eapply Mem.store_unchanged_on; eauto.
       unfold loc_unmapped'.
       repeat intro.
       destruct H1. unfold loc_unmapped in H3.
       congruence.
    +
      eapply Mem.store_unchanged_on; eauto.
      unfold loc_out_of_reach',loc_out_of_reach; intros. red; intros.
      assert (EQ: Ptrofs.unsigned (Ptrofs.add i0 (Ptrofs.repr delta)) = Ptrofs.unsigned i0 + delta)
  by (eapply Mem.address_inject; eauto with mem).
  rewrite EQ in *.
  destruct H1 as [H1' H1].
  eelim H1; eauto.
  exploit Mem.store_valid_access_3. eexact STORE. intros [X Y].
  apply Mem.perm_cur_max. apply Mem.perm_implies with Writable; auto with mem.
  apply X. lia.
Qed.

  inv DIV'. constructor.

Lemma aval_inject_amaketotal:
  forall f (v v' : aval) g
         (INJREFL : forall x r, g x = Some r -> Val.inject f r r)
         (NOPTR : forall b o, g (Vptr b o) = None)

    aval_inject f v v' ->
    aval_inject f (amaketotal (alifto1 g v))
                (amaketotal (alifto1 g v')).
Proof.
  intros.
  inv H.
  - simpl.
    inv H0; repeat constructor.
    destruct ((g (Vint i))) eqn:GI; simpl; repeat constructor; eauto.
    destruct ((g (Vlong i))) eqn:GI; simpl; repeat constructor; eauto.
    destruct ((g (Vfloat f0))) eqn:GI; simpl; repeat constructor; eauto.
    destruct ((g (Vsingle f0))) eqn:GI; simpl; repeat constructor; eauto.
    rewrite NOPTR. rewrite NOPTR. simpl.
    repeat constructor.
    rewrite STRICT. simpl. destruct (g c'). simpl.
    repeat constructor.
    simpl. repeat constructor.
  - simpl. constructor. constructor.
Qed.

Lemma forallb_aval_eq_inject :
  forall f rs rs' (RINJ: aregset_inject f rs rs')
 l,
    forallb
      (fun r : mreg =>
         aval_eq (rs (preg_of r)) (Aval (Rval (Sreg (preg_of r)))))
      l = forallb
    (fun r : mreg =>
     aval_eq (rs' (preg_of r)) (Aval (Rval (Sreg (preg_of r)))))
    l.
Proof.
  induction l ; simpl; auto.
  f_equal.
  specialize (RINJ (preg_of a)).
  inv RINJ. inv H1; try reflexivity.
  reflexivity.
  auto.
Qed.


Lemma is_final_state_inject : forall f rs rs',
    aregset_inject f rs rs' ->
        is_final_state rs = is_final_state rs'.
Proof.
  unfold is_final_state.
  intros.
  f_equal. f_equal.
  specialize (H PC).
  inv H.
  inv H2; auto.
  reflexivity.
  specialize (H IR13).
  inv H.
  inv H2; auto.
  reflexivity.
  eapply forallb_aval_eq_inject; eauto.
Qed.


Lemma is_definedb_inject : forall f v v',
    is_definedb v = true ->
    Val.inject f v v' ->
    is_definedb v' = true.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite is_defined_inv in H.
  rewrite is_defined_inv.
  inv H0; congruence.
Qed.

Lemma has_type_inject : forall f v v' t,
    v <> Vundef ->
    Val.has_type v t ->
    Val.inject f v v' ->
    Val.has_type v' t.
Proof.
  intros. inv H1 ; simpl in *; auto.
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma has_rettypeb_inject : forall f v v' rt,
    v <> Vundef ->
    has_rettypeb v rt = true ->
    Val.inject f v v' ->
    has_rettypeb v' rt = true.
Proof.
  unfold has_rettypeb.
  intros.
  destruct rt; auto.
  -
    destruct (Val.has_type_dec v t).
    + eapply has_type_inject in H1; eauto.
      destruct (Val.has_type_dec v' t); auto.
    + destruct (Val.has_type_dec v' t); auto.
  - destruct v ; try congruence.
    inv H1. auto.
  - destruct v ; try congruence.
    inv H1. auto.
  - destruct v ; try congruence.
    inv H1. auto.
  - destruct v ; try congruence.
    inv H1. auto.
  - destruct v ; try congruence.
Qed.

Lemma get_result_inject :
  forall f rt r m1 vres m2 m1' rs rs'
         (BEXEC : get_result rt (rs r) m1 = Some (vres, m2) )
         (INJ : Mem.inject f m1 m1')
         (VINJ : aregset_inject f rs rs'),
  exists (vres' : val) (m2' : mem),
    get_result rt (rs' r) m1' = Some (vres', m2') /\
    Val.inject f vres vres' /\
    Mem.inject f m2 m2' /\
    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_unmapped' f m1) m1 m2 /\
    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_reach' f m1 m1') m1' m2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold get_result in BEXEC.
  specialize (VINJ r).
  destruct (rs r);try discriminate.
  inv VINJ.
  destruct (is_definedb v && has_rettypeb v rt) eqn:D ; try discriminate.
  rewrite andb_true_iff in D.
  destruct D as (D & TYP).
  unfold get_result.
  erewrite is_definedb_inject ; eauto.
  rewrite is_defined_inv in D.
  erewrite has_rettypeb_inject ; eauto.
  inv BEXEC.
  do 3 eexists ; split_and ; try reflexivity.
  eauto. auto.
  apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
  apply Mem.unchanged_on_refl.
Qed.


Lemma find_instr_inject : forall f v v' m m' i,
    find_instr v m = Some i ->
    aval_inject f v v' ->
    Mem.inject f m m' ->
    find_instr v' m' = Some i.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold find_instr, BinDecode.find_instr in *.
  inv H0; try discriminate.
  destruct (Mem.loadv Mint16unsigned m c) eqn:LV ; try discriminate.
  destruct v ; try discriminate.
  exploit Mem.loadv_inject;eauto.
  intros (v2 & LOAD & LD).
  rewrite LOAD. inv LD.
  destruct (is_thumb2 i0); auto.
  destruct_in H eq:LV1 ; try discriminate.
  destruct v; try discriminate.
  exploit Mem.loadv_inject;eauto with inject.
  intros (v3 & LOAD3 & LD3).
  rewrite LOAD3.
  inv LD3. congruence.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_load_same_block :
  forall w c v i rs stk stkb m1 rs' stk' stkb' m2,
         aexec_load w c v i rs stk stkb m1 =
           ANext rs' stk' stkb' m2 ->
  stkb = stkb'.
Proof.
  unfold aexec_load.
  destruct v; try discriminate.
  destruct a ; try discriminate.
  - intros. destruct (Mem.loadv c m1 v); try discriminate.
    congruence.
  - destruct (get_stack_offset v); try discriminate.
    intros.
    destruct (astack_load c m1 stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i)); congruence.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_store_same_block :
  forall w c a i rs stk stkb rs' stk' stkb' m1 m2,
    aexec_store w c a i rs stk stkb m1 = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m2 ->
    stkb = stkb'.
Proof.
  unfold aexec_store,aexec_store'.
  intros.
  destruct a; try congruence.
  destruct (is_stack_pointer stkb a); try discriminate.
  - destruct (astack_store c m1 stk stkb (Ptrofs.unsigned i0) (rs i)); congruence.
  -
    destruct a ; try congruence.
    destruct (rs i) ; try congruence.
    destruct (Mem.storev c m1 v v0); try congruence.
Qed.

Lemma aexec_instr_same_stkb :
  forall w i rs stk stkb stkb' m1 rs' stk' m2,
    aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m1 = ANext rs' stk' stkb' m2 ->
    stkb = stkb'.
Proof.
  unfold aexec_instr. intros.
  destruct i; try congruence; try (eapply aexec_load_same_block; eauto ; fail);
    try (eapply aexec_store_same_block; eauto ; fail).
  - destruct (aadd (rs i0) (aeval_shift_op s rs)); congruence.
  - unfold agoto_label in H.
    congruence.
  - destruct (aeval_testcond t rs); try congruence.
    destruct b ; inv H; congruence.
  - destruct (aadd (alift2 Val.mul (rs i0) (rs i1)) (rs i2)); congruence.
  - destruct (adivs (rs IR0) (rs IR1)); congruence.
  - destruct (adivu (rs IR0) (rs IR1)); congruence.
Qed.

Lemma bin_interp_inject :
  forall n rt stk stk' stkb stkb' f rs rs' m1 m1' vres m2
         (BEXEC : bin_interp rt n rs stk stkb m1 = Some (vres,m2))
         (INJ : Mem.inject f m1 m1')
         (SINJ : astack_inject f stk stk')
         (VINJ : aregset_inject f rs rs')
         (FB : inj_stack stkb stkb' f )
  ,
  exists (vres' : val) (m2' : mem),
    bin_interp rt n rs' stk' stkb' m1' = Some(vres', m2') /\
    Val.inject f vres vres' /\
    Mem.inject f m2 m2' /\
    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_unmapped' f m1) m1 m2 /\
    Mem.unchanged_on (loc_out_of_reach' f m1 m1') m1' m2'.
Proof.
  induction n.
  - simpl. intros.
    exploit is_final_state_inject ; eauto.
    intro RFINAL.
    rewrite RFINAL in BEXEC.
    destruct (is_final_state rs') eqn:FINAL; try discriminate.
    eapply get_result_inject; eauto.
  - intros.
    simpl in BEXEC.
    exploit is_final_state_inject ; eauto.
    intro RFINAL.
    rewrite RFINAL in BEXEC.
    simpl.
    destruct (is_final_state rs').
    + eapply get_result_inject; eauto.
    + destruct (find_instr (rs PC) m1) as [(i,w)|] eqn:FINSTR ; try discriminate.
      eapply find_instr_inject in FINSTR; eauto.
      rewrite FINSTR.
      destruct (aexec_instr w i rs stk stkb m1) eqn: AEXEC ; try discriminate.
      exploit aexec_instr_same_stkb; eauto.
      intro. subst b.
      exploit aexec_instr_inject ; eauto.
      intros (rs2' & stk2' & stkb2' & m2' &
                EXEC & RIN' & SINJ' & MINJ' & U1 & U2).
      rewrite EXEC.
      exploit aexec_instr_same_stkb. apply EXEC. intro; subst.
      exploit IHn; eauto.
      intros (vres' & mres & IN & VINJ1 & VINJ2 & U1' & U2').
      do 2 eexists; split_and ; eauto.
      * eapply Mem.unchanged_on_trans ; eauto.
      eapply Mem.unchanged_on_implies; eauto.
      unfold loc_unmapped',loc_unmapped.
      intros.
      destruct H.
      split.
      exploit aexec_instr_nextblock.
      apply AEXEC.
      unfold Mem.valid_block in *. congruence.
      auto.
      * eapply Mem.unchanged_on_trans ; eauto.
      eapply Mem.unchanged_on_implies; eauto.
      unfold loc_out_of_reach',loc_out_of_reach.
      intros.
      destruct H.
      split.
      exploit aexec_instr_nextblock.
      apply EXEC.
      unfold Mem.valid_block in *. congruence.
      intros.
      intro.
      eapply H1; eauto.
      eapply aexec_instr_perm;eauto.
Qed.


Lemma init_state_not_valid_block :
  forall s sz pos vargs m1 rs stk stkb m2,
    init_state s sz pos vargs m1 = ANext rs stk stkb m2 ->
    ~ Mem.valid_block m1 stkb.
Proof.
  unfold init_state.
  intros.
  destruct (alloc_arguments vargs (sig_args s) int_param_regs);
    try discriminate.
  destruct_in H eq:AF; try discriminate.
  inv H. exploit allocframe_mem;eauto.
  rewrite AF. congruence.
  intros (rs' & stk' & AF').
  rewrite AF in AF'.
  destruct (Mem.alloc m1 0 sz) eqn: ALLOC. inv AF'.
  eapply Mem.fresh_block_alloc. eauto.
Qed.



Lemma init_state_valid_block_inv :
  forall s sz pos vargs m1 rs stk stkb m2 b,
    init_state s sz pos vargs m1 = ANext rs stk stkb m2 ->
    Mem.valid_block m2 b ->
    (Mem.valid_block m1 b /\ b <> stkb) \/ b = stkb.
Proof.
  unfold init_state.
  intros.
  destruct (alloc_arguments vargs (sig_args s) int_param_regs);
    try discriminate.
  destruct_in H eq:AF; try discriminate.
  inv H. exploit allocframe_mem;eauto.
  rewrite AF. congruence.
  intros (rs' & stk' & AF').
  rewrite AF in AF'.
  destruct (Mem.alloc m1 0 sz) eqn: ALLOC. inv AF'.
  apply Mem.valid_block_alloc_inv with (b':=b) in ALLOC; auto.
  tauto.
Qed.

Lemma bin_exec_sem_inject :
  forall n s sz pos ge1 ge2 f vargs vargs' m1 m1' t vres m2
         (BEXEC : bin_exec_sem n s sz pos ge1 vargs m1 t vres m2)
         (INJ : Mem.inject f m1 m1')

  exists f'.
  do 2 eexists.
  split_and.
  - econstructor. reflexivity.

    rewrite I.

  - eauto.
  - eauto.

    repeat intro.
    split ; auto.
    destruct H.
    destruct (eq_block b b0).
    * subst.
    destruct (f' b0) eqn: F';[|now auto].
    destruct p.
    exfalso.

    * erewrite <- augment_not_alloc; eauto.
      constructor ; eauto.
